This 2019 Chevrolet Tahoe LT is a standout in its class, boasting an impressive array of features that cater to your every need. Let's dive into what makes this SUV a must-have.

• Freshly Serviced
• Flawless CARFAX
• SUN, ENTERTAINMENT AND DESTINATIONS PACKAGE
• RST EDITION
• SEATS, SECOND ROW BUCKET, MANUAL
• MAX TRAILERING PACKAGE
• LPO, ALL-WEATHER FLOOR LINER, 1ST AND 2ND ROWS
• MOLDINGS, BODY-COLOR BODYSIDE

The Tahoe LT is equipped with the powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, delivering a smooth and responsive driving experience. With 4-wheel drive and a 6-speed automatic transmission, you'll have the capability to tackle any terrain with confidence. And with an impressive fuel economy of 15 city/21 highway MPG, you can enjoy your adventures without constantly stopping at the pump.

But the Tahoe LT is more than just a capable performer – it's also a technological powerhouse. Featuring the Chevrolet Infotainment system with an 8-inch color touchscreen, you'll have access to navigation, SiriusXM radio, and seamless integration with your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The premium audio system and rear-seat entertainment system ensure that everyone in the family will be entertained on long drives.

Safety is also a top priority in the Tahoe LT. With features like Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist, and Low Speed Forward Automatic Braking, you can drive with confidence knowing that your vehicle is looking out for you and your loved ones.

This Tahoe LT is a certified pre-owned vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty. You can rest assured that you're getting a high-quality, reliable SUV that will serve you well for years to come.

Family owned, servicing Washington, Wheeling, Morgantown and the surrounding areas since 1975.

description:
Meet the 2019 Subaru Forester Base—the kind of car that doesn’t shout for attention because it doesn’t have to.
Confidently understated, this Forester pairs Subaru’s legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive with a clean, practical design that feels just as at home in the city as it does escaping it. The cabin is airy, thoughtfully laid out, and refreshingly honest—everything where it should be, nothing pretending to be something it’s not. Visibility is excellent, the ride is composed, and the driving experience is calm, capable, and quietly reassuring.
This is a vehicle for people who value substance over flash. For those who appreciate safety, reliability, and versatility wrapped in a smart, modern package. Whether it’s daily commuting, weekend errands, or spontaneous road trips, the Forester shows up ready—no drama, no fuss, just competence with character.
In short: a sophisticated all-rounder with a subtle sense of humor and a very dependable backbone.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2019 Honda Passport Touring. Boasting a powerful 3.5L V6 engine, this SUV delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 20 city/25 highway MPG rating. Dressed in a sleek and sophisticated exterior, the Passport Touring exudes a commanding presence on the road.

• Navigation system: Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System
• 10 Speakers
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System warning
• Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS) + FCW mitigation
• Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) active
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Leather-Trimmed Seats
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• Heated rear seats
• Power Liftgate

Step inside the Passport Touring and experience the epitome of luxury and convenience. The spacious cabin is adorned with premium leather-trimmed seats, offering unparalleled comfort and style. The 10-speaker premium audio system delivers an immersive listening experience, while the Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System ensures you always arrive at your destination with ease.

Safety is paramount in the Passport Touring, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including the Collision Mitigation Braking System, Lane Keeping Assist System, and Blind Spot Information System. These cutting-edge features work seamlessly to provide you and your passengers with the utmost protection on the road.

Elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures with the 2019 Honda Passport Touring. This versatile SUV combines powerful performance, exceptional fuel efficiency, and a wealth of premium features to deliver an unrivaled driving experience. Discover the perfect balance of capability, comfort, and convenience in this stunning vehicle.

We understand that finding the right vehicle can be a daunting task, but we're here to make the process as smooth and enjoyable as possible. Our Market Based Pricing approach ensures a hassle-free experience, a faster buying process, and the confidence that you're not overpaying. We've done the research for you, so you can focus on finding the perfect fit.

We offer Market Based Pricing. What that means for you, 1. Hassle-Free Experience 2. Faster Buying Process 3. Confidence in Not Overpaying and 4. We do the Research for you. Vehicle Details
2019 Jeep Wrangler Sport 4WD — bold capability meets everyday comfort in Jackson, GA. This rugged V6 3.6L gasoline Jeep Wrangler Sport delivers proven off-road performance and smooth on-road handling, backed by a CARFAX Clean Report for confidence. If you're searching for the best price on a dependable, adventure-ready SUV, this Jeep Wrangler checks every box. Equipped with a rock-solid 4WD system and a torquey 3.6L V6, it's built to tackle mud, sand, and snow while still providing a comfortable commute. The Sport trim focuses on essential features drivers need: Hands Free Bluetooth for seamless calling and audio streaming, Satellite and XM Radio for endless entertainment on the go, and a Back-Up Camera to make parking and trailhead maneuvers easier. This Jeep Wrangler's rugged exterior and functional interior are ideal for weekend warriors and daily drivers alike. Seating offers comfort and durability, while the open-air capability turns any drive into an outdoor experience. Safety-minded buyers will appreciate the documented maintenance history and the CARFAX Clean Report, which confirms a trustworthy vehicle background. Located in Jackson, GA and priced to move, this 2019 Jeep Wrangler Sport represents exceptional value for buyers who want the Jeep lifestyle without breaking the bank. Schedule a test drive today and see why this Jeep Wrangler is the smart choice for capability, comfort, and the best price in the area.

Equipment
This 1/2 ton suv is equipped with the latest generation of XM/Sirius Radio. This 2019 Jeep Wrangler has satellite radio capabilities. Bluetooth technology is built into the vehicle, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. See what's behind you with the back up camera on the vehicle. The Jeep Wrangler has a clean CARFAX vehicle history report. The Jeep Wrangler has four wheel drive capabilities. This unit has a V6, 3.6L high output engine. This model emanates grace with its stylish gray exterior. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in it is easy with the climate control system. With the adjustable lumbar support in this 2019 Jeep Wrangler your back will love you. This 2019 Jeep Wrangler features cruise control for long trips. The Electronic Stability Control will keep you on your intended path. The fog lights cut through the weather so you can see what's ahead.See what's behind you with the back up camera on it.

Vehicle Details
2019 Nissan Armada SL — powerful V8 performance meets premium comfort in this well-equipped full-size SUV, located in Santa Fe, NM. Powered by a robust 5.6L V8 gasoline engine with rear-wheel drive, this Nissan Armada SL delivers confident towing capability and smooth highway cruising while offering spacious seating for families and groups. This Nissan Armada SL includes Navigation for effortless route guidance across New Mexico and beyond, Forward Collision Warning for added safety on busy roads, and a convenient Back-Up Camera to simplify parking and trailer hookups. The interior features upscale touches and a BOSE stereo system that provides exceptional audio clarity for every drive. Practical technology and comfort options are combined with durable engineering to create a reliable daily driver or weekend adventure vehicle. Buy with confidence — this SUV comes with a CARFAX Clean Report, reflecting a well-maintained history that supports long-term ownership value. Priced to move, this Nissan Armada is offered at the best price in the area, delivering exceptional value compared to similar listings. Whether you need towing strength, passenger comfort, or advanced safety features, the 2019 Nissan Armada SL in Santa Fe, NM is a compelling choice. Contact us to schedule a test drive and see why this Nissan Armada SL stands out among pre-owned SUVs in the region.

Equipment
Never get into a cold vehicle again with the remote start feature on the vehicle. It keeps you comfortable with Auto Climate. It features a high end BOSE stereo system. You'll never again be lost in a crowded city or a country region with the navigation system on the Nissan Armada. The rear parking assist technology on the Nissan Armada will put you at ease when reversing. The system alerts you as you get closer to an obstruction. This 1/2 ton suv has a clean CARFAX vehicle history report. The leather seats in the vehicle are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. See what's behind you with the back up camera on the vehicle. Bluetooth technology is built into this vehicle, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. The Nissan Armada's Forward Collision Warning feature alerts drivers to potential front-end collisions.

Safety is paramount, with features like blind spot monitoring, lane keeping assist, and cross-traffic alert providing peace of mind. The integrated turn signal mirrors and automatic high beams enhance visibility, ensuring a secure drive. With its smart device integration and WiFi hotspot, the RDX keeps you connected, making it the ideal choice for the modern driver seeking both luxury and practicality. Be sure to call or visit Trophy Nissan to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera with washer - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. Even if there are sloppy conditions, the washer keeps the camera's view clean. Rear camera with washer is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

The 2019 Chevrolet Suburban LT is a remarkable SUV that seamlessly blends luxury, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This versatile vehicle is available with several impressive packages, including the Texas Edition Package, Z71 Midnight Edition, Body Security Content Theft-Protection Package, Interior Protection Package, and Preferred Equipment Group 1LT, making it an ideal choice for families and adventurers alike.

Under the hood, the Suburban LT is powered by the EcoTec3 5.3L V-8 engine, featuring gasoline direct injection and variable valve control, producing an impressive 355 horsepower. This powerhouse is paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, ensuring a perfect balance of performance and efficiency for both city drives and long road trips.

The Texas Edition Package is particularly noteworthy, offering a range of features that elevate convenience and comfort. With a power liftgate rear cargo door, heated door mirrors, and flexible seating options including 60-40 folding second-row seats and a third-row split-bench seat, the Suburban LT accommodates both passengers and cargo with ease.

Safety is paramount in the Suburban LT. It comes equipped with advanced features such as forward collision mitigation, which detects potential collisions and prepares the vehicle and occupants for impact, enhancing overall safety. Additionally, lane departure prevention technology ensures you stay within your lane, providing peace of mind during long journeys.

Entertainment is a key focus as well, with a rear entertainment system featuring Blu-ray and digital media to keep passengers entertained on any trip. The smart device mirroring feature allows easy integration of your smartphone with the vehicle’s infotainment system, enhancing your driving experience.

Connectivity reaches new heights with the built-in mobile hotspot, enabling you to stay connected to the internet without draining your mobile data. This feature is particularly useful for families on the go, ensuring that everyone can enjoy their favorite online content.

In summary, the 2019 Chevrolet Suburban LT stands out in the full-size SUV segment with its luxurious interior, powerful engine, and a plethora of advanced features. Whether you’re navigating city streets or embarking on an exciting family adventure, this SUV is designed to meet your needs while keeping everyone safe and entertained. Experience the perfect combination of style, comfort, and functionality with the Suburban LT.

description:
The 2019 Mercedes Benz GLC 300 delivers refined luxury smooth performance and everyday versatility in a compact luxury SUV designed for daily commuting professional use and long term ownership value. With 87726 miles this GLC reflects consistent responsible use while continuing to offer dependable performance supported by Mercedes Benz engineering. Power comes from a turbocharged four cylinder engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission that provides responsive acceleration quiet cruising and confident highway performance. The suspension tuning delivers a composed comfortable ride with precise handling that feels secure during city driving highway travel and longer trips.

Inside the GLC 300 offers a sophisticated well crafted cabin focused on comfort quality and driver confidence. Leather appointed seating heated front seats and a power adjustable driver seat with memory create a refined driving environment. The interior layout provides excellent headroom and legroom for both front and rear passengers while the split folding rear seats expand cargo capacity for luggage groceries work equipment or travel gear. Premium materials brushed metal accents and clean dashboard lines reflect the attention to detail expected from the Mercedes Benz brand.

Technology in the 2019 GLC 300 is intuitive modern and driver focused. A central color display anchors the Mercedes Benz infotainment system with navigation Bluetooth connectivity smartphone integration and voice command capability. Steering wheel mounted controls keep audio phone and cruise functions easily accessible while maintaining focus on the road. Push button start keyless entry dual zone automatic climate control and a premium audio system add everyday convenience and comfort. A digital driver information display provides clear real time vehicle data.

Safety remains a strong advantage of the GLC lineup. This model includes forward collision warning automatic emergency braking blind spot monitoring attention assist stability control traction control antilock braking and a comprehensive airbag system. The rigid safety structure and advanced braking systems contribute to confident driving in traffic highway conditions and changing road environments. The elevated seating position enhances outward visibility and overall driver awareness.

The exterior of the 2019 Mercedes Benz GLC 300 features sleek sculpted body lines LED lighting alloy wheels and the signature Mercedes Benz grille. The refined proportions and athletic stance deliver a confident upscale road presence suitable for both personal and professional use. Its combination of turbocharged performance premium interior comfort advanced safety features and proven reliability makes the GLC 300 a strong choice for drivers seeking a value driven luxury SUV with everyday usability and refined style.

Why Buy from Jackie Cooper Nissan
Every used vehicle on our lot goes through a strenuous 150 point inspection before it is ever offered for sale because quality and safety are part of our heritage. Our factory trained technicians examine all major systems including engine transmission brakes suspension tires and electrical components to ensure each vehicle meets our high standards for performance and reliability. We also inspect for signs of prior damage mechanical issues and cosmetic wear inside and out. If something does not meet our strict criteria it is either repaired or replaced before the vehicle reaches the lot. This careful process reflects our commitment to your peace of mind because you deserve a vehicle you can count on.

description:
The 2019 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport S 4x4 is an exceptional choice for adventure enthusiasts, seamlessly merging off-road capability with cutting-edge technology. This rugged SUV offers an impressive array of features, particularly highlighted in the Quick Order Package 28S Sport S and the Technology Group, each crafted to elevate your driving experience.

Under the hood, you’ll find a robust 2L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, delivering an impressive 270HP. This powerhouse is coupled with a TorqueFlite 8-speed automatic transmission, ensuring smooth acceleration and performance across various terrains, whether you’re navigating city streets or tackling challenging trails.

The Quick Order Package 28S Sport S enhances your journey with premium features such as power door mirrors and heated side mirrors, ensuring clear visibility in all weather conditions. The leather steering wheel adds a touch of luxury, while keyless entry and auto-locking doors provide convenience and security. Illuminated entry is an elegant touch that welcomes you into your Jeep, making nighttime access effortless.

For tech-savvy drivers, the Technology Group is indispensable. It includes automatic climate control with dual-zone settings, allowing you and your passengers to customize your comfort. The 7-inch primary display supports Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, facilitating smart device mirroring that keeps you connected without diverting your attention from the road. Wireless connectivity enables hands-free calling, promoting safety during your travels.

Moreover, the Wrangler Unlimited Sport S prioritizes practical features that enhance safety and convenience. The rear camera ensures better visibility when reversing, while brake assist technology provides enhanced stopping power in urgent situations. Comfort is paramount, with cloth seat upholstery and a 6-way adjustable driver seat, making both short commutes and long journeys enjoyable.

In summary, the 2019 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport S 4x4 stands out as a remarkable vehicle for those who seek adventure without compromising on comfort or connectivity. With its powerful performance and thoughtful features, it’s ready to accompany you on your next exploration. Discover the potential of this outstanding Jeep and prepare for unforgettable journeys!

description:
Discover the ultimate adventure-ready SUV with the 2019 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara. This iconic off-road warrior combines rugged capability, sophisticated design, and a wealth of premium features to elevate your driving experience.

Equipped with a potent 2.0L I4 Turbocharged eTorque engine, this Wrangler delivers impressive power and efficiency, with 22 city/24 highway MPG. Paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, it's ready to tackle any terrain with confidence.

• 8-Speed Automatic Transmission
• Black 3-Piece Hard Top
• Safety Group (Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection, ParkSense Rear Park Assist System)
• Quick Order Package 28G

The Sahara's striking white exterior complements the premium interior, featuring cloth low-back bucket seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a host of advanced technology. Enjoy seamless connectivity with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, while the ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera and Blind Spot Monitoring provide added peace of mind.

Designed to conquer the toughest terrain, the Wrangler Unlimited Sahara boasts a Heavy Duty Suspension with Gas Shocks, 4-Wheel Disc Brakes, and Traction Control. Whether you're navigating winding mountain roads or tackling rugged off-road trails, this Jeep is ready to take you there in style and comfort.

Imagine the thrill of owning a true American icon, built to withstand the demands of your adventurous lifestyle. The 2019 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is the perfect blend of capability, technology, and refinement, ready to elevate your driving experience to new heights.

The moment you walk into Zeller Motors in Arkansas City KS, you're going to feel like part of the family. For more than 50 years, we've been offering ways to make car buying easier. This 2019 Volkswagen Atlas 3.6L V6 SEL Pure White with a Shetland Beige interior. This Volkswagen Atlas comes with the following features: Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending rear collision.
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
  • An active blind spot system helps prevent the driver from making a lane change when another vehicle is in their blind spot.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
This Volkswagen Atlas comes with the following packages: We invite you to shop our new inventory or our used cars to find the car, truck, SUV or minivan you're interested in. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and comfort in this 2019 GMC Terrain SLT. With its sleek exterior, turbocharged engine, and a wealth of premium features, this SUV is designed to elevate your driving experience.

• 2.0L Turbocharged I-4 Engine
• Preferred Package (Hands-Free Rear Power Programmable Liftgate, Memory Package, Front Passenger 6-Way Power Seat, Heated Steering Wheel, Universal Home Remote)
• Driver Alert Package I (Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, Rear Park Assist, Safety Alert Seat)
• 19" Machined Aluminum Wheels with Gray Accents
• Perforated Leather-Appointed Seat Trim
• Heated Front Seats
• Power Driver Lumbar Control
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Hands-Free Rear Power Programmable Liftgate
• Rear Cross-Traffic Alert
• Safety Alert Seat

This Terrain SLT offers the perfect balance of power and efficiency, with a 2.0L turbocharged engine that delivers 252 horsepower and 260 lb-ft of torque, while still achieving an impressive 22 city/28 highway MPG. The 9-speed automatic transmission provides smooth, responsive acceleration and efficient highway cruising.

Inside, the Terrain SLT surrounds you in premium comfort and convenience. The perforated leather-appointed seats are both stylish and supportive, while the heated front seats and heated steering wheel ensure you stay cozy on even the chilliest days. The Preferred Package adds a host of desirable features, including a hands-free power liftgate, memory settings for the driver's seat and mirrors, and a universal garage door opener.

For added peace of mind, the Driver Alert Package I equips the Terrain with advanced safety technologies like Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and the Safety Alert Seat, which uses subtle vibrations to warn you of potential hazards.

With its bold, sculpted design, turbocharged performance, and impressive array of premium features, this 2019 GMC Terrain SLT is the perfect choice for the discerning SUV buyer. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional value and driving enjoyment this Terrain has to offer.

Oklahoma City’s local INFINITI dealer, Bob Moore INFINITI, is here for all your auto needs. We serve all the Oklahoma City metro including Oklahoma City, Edmond, Moore, Norman, and more. If you’re looking for a local car dealership that offers new INFINITIs, used vehicles of all makes and models, exceptional service, and multiple finance options we’ve got you covered. Looking for used vehicles for sale in Oklahoma City? At Bob Moore INFINITI we have a large assortment of used vehicles including a variety of makes and models. While we carry many used makes and models, we also carry used INFINITIs in case you aren’t looking for new models. If you’re still trying to decide which model and trim is the best fit, we can get you with one of our certified INFINITI specialists to go over all the details — whether it’s regarding features, warranties, service, financing, or any other areas you’d like addressed. Our dealership also offers a variety of amenities, free Wi-Fi, and all kinds of perks. For those wishing to shop for their car online, we can help you with that as well. All our inventory is held on our website where you can complete the whole purchase process. If you’d like to visit the dealership but need assistance getting there, we offer free valet service within 30 minutes of our store and give free at-home delivery. If you need to schedule any of these services, please call our dealership.
When buying an used vehicle, we want to make sure you get your money’s worth. To ensure this, we put all our used vehicles through a service reconditioning process. This process includes a 106-point inspection of the vehicle to ensure that it’s up to our standards. We make sure the tires have three 30-second tire depths or 30%, if they don’t, we’ll replace the tires. We’ll also replace any brakes over 3mm. After the vehicles full inspection, it leaves the shop and goes through cosmetic refurbishing where we inspect and replace scratches, dents, scuffs, and road rash, as well as interior leather and upholstery reconditioning. While we work hard to ensure the quality of all used vehicles, we must acknowledge that some will end up with defects. Speak with one of our sales specialists about an used vehicle you’re interested in to get a history of the car. Bob Moore also covers all your INFINITI, and any other make or model, service needs with our factory trained technicians, including 4 master certified technicians. This includes a complimentary car wash and vacuum with every service. Prior to your service, contact our dealership team to get your service appointment set up. Financing a vehicle purchase can be a stressful process but Bob Moore INFINITI offers a seamless auto financing, with over 20 lenders to work with. This helps us ensure that we’re getting you the best deal possible for your new car. If you have any questions when going through the financing, don’t stress. We’ll have our INFINITI finance expert there with you to answer any questions or concerns you might have. Do you need to trade in your current vehicle? We buy cars too. Whether it’s a trade-in for a new purchase or just simply selling your vehicle, we’d love to work with you.

description:
Discover the pinnacle of modern SUV design with this stunning 2019 GMC Acadia Denali. Meticulously crafted to deliver unparalleled performance, comfort, and technology, this Acadia Denali is the ultimate expression of GMC's commitment to excellence.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this Acadia Denali is truly a cut above the rest. Highlights include:

• Technology Package, featuring Surround Vision, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Forward Automatic Braking
• Dual SkyScape 2-Panel Power Sunroof
• Power Liftgate
• Bose Premium 8-Speaker Sound System
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Seats
• Perforated Leather-Appointed Seating

The 3.6L V6 SIDI engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 MPG on the highway. Whether navigating the daily commute or embarking on a family adventure, this Acadia Denali is a true masterpiece of engineering, offering a driving experience that is both exhilarating and refined.

Beyond its impressive performance, this Acadia Denali is also a technological marvel, boasting a suite of advanced features designed to keep you connected, entertained, and safe. The GMC Infotainment System with Navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration ensures seamless connectivity, while the Surround Vision camera system and Forward Automatic Braking provide an extra layer of confidence on the road.

Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, the Acadia Denali's exterior is a true head-turner, with its sleek, aerodynamic lines and stunning White Frost Tricoat finish. The 20-inch polished aluminum wheels and chrome accents add a touch of sophistication, while the power liftgate and roof rails provide exceptional versatility for all your cargo-carrying needs.

Step inside the Acadia Denali, and you'll be greeted by a spacious, luxuriously appointed cabin that exudes refinement. The heated and ventilated front seats, along with the heated rear seats, ensure maximum comfort for all passengers, while the Bose premium audio system delivers an immersive listening experience.

With its uncompromising blend of power, technology, and style, this 2019 GMC Acadia Denali is the ultimate expression of modern SUV design. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the exceptional value and exceptional driving experience this Acadia Denali has to offer.

Command attention with our One Owner 2019 Toyota Highlander XLE AWD in Midnight Black Metallic! Powered by a 3.5 Liter V6 that provides 295hp connected to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission for bold driving authority. This All Wheel Drive SUV also returns nearly 26mpg on the highway with a modern and muscular design. In addition, our Highlander's LED lighting, fog lamps, a power sunroof, power liftgate, roof rails, alloy wheels, and heated power mirrors look even better in person!

Spacious and comfortable, our XLE cabin is ready for fantastic family travel with heated leather front seats, eight-way power for the driver, flexible second and third rows, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, tri-zone automatic climate control, and a Smart Key system with pushbutton ignition. Full-color navigation helps you stay on track in our Highlander, which features further tech benefits like an 8-inch touchscreen, voice control, Bluetooth, a six-speaker sound system, and a Driver Easy Speak intercom.

Toyota takes care of you and your loved ones with a rearview camera, blind-spot monitoring, and Safety Sense systems such as automatic braking, lane-keeping assistance, adaptive cruise control, and more. It's easy to see why so many people recommend our Highlander XLE for happier trails! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

Sportier & More Engaging Driving FeelRear-wheel drive gives the GLC300 a more balanced and dynamic handling character compared with front-biased AWD systems. Many drivers find RWD SUVs feel more connected and responsive in normal driving.The naturally balanced weight distribution and RWD layout contribute to crisp turn-in and predictable handling on dry pavement.2. Better Fuel EconomyThe RWD version typically edges out the AWD variant in efficiency. According to EPA estimates, the GLC300 RWD is rated around 22 city / 28 highway mpg, slightly better than the AWD version.3. Lower Purchase Price & Ownership CostRWD is the base drivetrain for 2019 GLC300, so its MSRP is usually lower than GLC300 4MATIC AWD. This can mean lower upfront cost and potentially lower insurance costs vs AWD.Simpler drivetrain (no AWD hardware) means fewer components that could require maintenance or repair over time.4. Adequate Power & Smooth AutoPowered by a 241-hp 2.0 L turbo four-cylinder with a 9-speed automatic, the GLC300 has confident acceleration for everyday driving.Rear-wheel drive can make the most of that power in dry conditions, offering smooth launches and predictable throttle behavior.5. Comfortable Ride & Luxury CabinThe GLC300 delivers a comfortable and well-damped ride, with quality interior materials and a premium feel expected of Mercedes-Benz.Standard features include a supportive drivers seat, refined cabin design, and a user-friendly infotainment interface.6. Drive Mode FlexibilityThe DYNAMIC SELECT system (with ECO, Comfort, Sport, Sport+, and Individual modes) lets you tailor throttle response, transmission shifts, and steering feel. This makes the GLC300 RWD feel versatile from relaxed cruising to a livelier drive.7. Weight AdvantageWithout AWD hardware, the RWD variant is generally lighter. Lower weight can improve acceleration, braking, and help marginally with efficiency and handling balance.Every used vehicle on our lot goes through a strenuous, multi-point inspection before its ever offered for sale because quality and safety aren't just priorities for us, they're part of our heritage. We also inspect for signs of prior damage, mechanical issues, and cosmetic wear, inside and out.   • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.

  • This upholstery simulates leather, is durable and easy to keep clean.
  • Fixed third-row seats
  • Power reclining driver seat - Lean back. Gain some space between you and the wheel with power reclining driver seat. It lets you adjust the angle of the seatback at the touch of a button for added comfort while you're driving, or for a more comfortable rest while you're pulled over. Settle in, with power reclining driver seat.
  • Power reclining driver seat - Lean back. Gain some space between you and the wheel with power reclining driver seat. It lets you adjust the angle of the seatback at the touch of a button for added comfort while you're driving, or for a more comfortable rest while you're pulled over. Settle in, with power reclining driver seat.
Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
  • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
In-car Entertainment
  • Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...we're talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • All wheel drive - all weather drive. In wet or slippery conditions the more grip your wheels can maintain, the safer your drive. All wheel drive powers both the front and rear axles, allowing the center differential to redirect power to the wheels with greater traction when slip is detected. So get a firm grip on the road, better acceleration and added peace of mind in poor weather conditions with all-wheel drive.
  • All wheel drive - all weather drive. In wet or slippery conditions the more grip your wheels can maintain, the safer your drive. All wheel drive powers both the front and rear axles, allowing the center differential to redirect power to the wheels with greater traction when slip is detected. So get a firm grip on the road, better acceleration and added peace of mind in poor weather conditions with all-wheel drive.
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Rear collision mitigation - It has your back. Rear collision mitigation uses sensors to monitor the area behind you. If it senses an impending crash, it activates certain features to help prevent a collision or reduce the severity of it. Put your worries behind you with rear collision mitigation.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Active blind spot system - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. An active blind spot system not only alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear but helps prevent you from making an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with the confidence and safety of the Active blind spot system.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

This 2019 Chevrolet Traverse High Country is a premium three-row SUV built for families who want full-size comfort, upscale styling, and everyday versatility. Finished in Iridescent Pearl Tricoat with a Jet Black/Loft Brown interior, it delivers a refined look with a spacious cabin that’s ideal for commuting, road trips, and cargo needs.

Powered by a 3.6L V6 engine and paired with a 9-speed automatic transmission, this Traverse provides smooth acceleration, confident highway performance, and composed handling. The AWD system adds traction and stability in changing road and weather conditions, making it a strong all-season family SUV.

description:
The 2019 Toyota Highlander LE is a fantastic choice for those seeking a family-friendly SUV packed with advanced safety features and modern conveniences. With its sleek design and impressive capabilities, the Highlander LE is sure to meet your transportation needs.

One of the standout features of the Highlander LE is its **Forward Collision Mitigation** system. This innovative technology continuously scans the road ahead for potential dangers, automatically activating safety measures to help prevent or minimize the severity of collisions. Coupled with the **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention** system, which detects pedestrians and assists in avoiding accidents, the Highlander LE prioritizes safety for both passengers and pedestrians alike.

Another impressive aspect is the **Rear Camera**, providing a clear view of obstacles behind the vehicle. This feature enhances parking and maneuvering in tight spaces, giving drivers added confidence. Additionally, the **Lane Departure Prevention** system offers invaluable assistance by correcting any unintended lane drifts, ensuring you stay safely within your lane during long drives or busy traffic.

For those road warriors, the **Adaptive Cruise Control** is a game-changer. It allows you to set your desired speed while automatically adjusting to maintain a safe distance from the vehicle ahead. This feature not only enhances comfort during long trips but also works hand-in-hand with the **Brake Assist**, which boosts stopping power in emergencies, ensuring your safety is always prioritized.

The Highlander LE also features **Selective Internet Access**, allowing you to customize your infotainment experience with real-time updates on sports, weather, or news—keeping you informed without distractions. Plus, with **Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls**, managing your speed on long journeys is easier than ever, helping reduce driver fatigue.

Finally, the intuitive **Touchscreen** interface makes accessing various features a breeze. With everything at your fingertips, you can focus more on enjoying the drive rather than fumbling with buttons.

In summary, the 2019 Toyota Highlander LE stands out for its robust safety features, modern technology, and family-oriented design. Whether youre commuting, running errands, or embarking on a family adventure, this SUV is equipped to handle it all. With a blend of cutting-edge technology and comfort, the Highlander LE is ready to elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Technology highlights include a high-resolution infotainment system, back-up camera, built-in WiFi hotspot, premium audio, and seamless smartphone integration. The Memory Package adds personalized settings for the drivers seat, mirrors, and steering wheel.

With the Trailering Package, this Acadia Denali is ready for weekend adventures, offering added versatility without sacrificing ride comfort or refinement.

This 2019 Kia Sportage EX is the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the exceptional value and quality this vehicle has to offer.

Powered by BMW’s 2.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-4 producing 248 hp and 258 lb-ft of torque, this sDrive model delivers engaging acceleration and efficient highway cruising. It’s mated to BMW’s smooth-shifting 8-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel-drive (sDrive) configuration for a balanced driving feel. EPA fuel economy is an excellent 23 MPG city and 30 MPG highway. Factory-equipped features (standard) - Powertrain and chassis: 2.0L turbocharged I4 (248 hp / 258 lb-ft), 8-speed Steptronic automatic transmission, sDrive rear-wheel drive, standard stability and traction control systems. - Exterior: Clean White finish, LED exterior lighting elements, power side mirrors, and alloy wheel construction from the factory for a refined appearance and durable ride. - Interior and comfort: Black interior color, power-adjustable front seats, split-folding rear seat for flexible cargo and passenger arrangements, automatic climate control (dual-zone), power windows and door locks, and a convenient power liftgate from the factory. - Infotainment and connectivity: BMW iDrive infotainment system with central display and rotary controller, Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming, USB connectivity for media and charging, and integrated audio system tuned to factory specifications. - Convenience and driver controls: Multi-function steering wheel controls, cruise control, keyless entry, and user-customizable driver settings via the iDrive system. - Safety and occupant protection: Comprehensive passive and active safety package including front and side-impact airbags, full-length curtain airbags, anti-lock braking system (ABS), electronic stability control, tire pressure monitoring, and a rearview camera—all standard equipment from the factory. Condition and history This X3 is in excellent overall condition and has been gently used, showing under 69,000 miles (an average of less than 9,000 miles per year). It has a clean CARFAX report and a single prior owner, reflecting responsible care and maintenance. This X3 sDrive30i blends BMW driving dynamics with practical SUV versatility and efficient fuel economy. description:
Experience the exceptional 2019 Toyota Highlander XLE, a versatile and sophisticated SUV that combines dynamic performance, advanced technology, and uncompromising comfort. This stunning red Highlander is the perfect blend of style and substance, ready to elevate your driving experience.

• Navigation System
• Automatic temperature control
• Front dual zone A/C
• Power driver seat
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Brake assist
• Electronic Stability Control
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Fully automatic headlights

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 engine and an 8-Speed Automatic Electronic transmission with ECT-i, the Highlander XLE delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an impressive 21 city and 27 highway MPG. Experience the confidence of Front-Wheel Drive, complemented by a sophisticated four-wheel independent suspension for a smooth and responsive ride.

Step inside the Highlander XLE and immerse yourself in a world of premium features. Sink into the luxurious leather-trimmed seats, where the driver's seat offers power adjustability for personalized comfort. Enjoy the convenience of the Entune Premium Audio system with Navigation and App Suite, keeping you connected and entertained on the go. The dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone on board can enjoy their ideal temperature, while the power moonroof and power liftgate add an extra touch of sophistication.

Safety is a top priority in the Highlander XLE, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Benefit from features like Brake Assist, Electronic Stability Control, and the Exterior Parking Camera Rear, providing you with peace of mind and confidence behind the wheel.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure, commuting in style, or seeking a versatile SUV to accommodate your lifestyle, the 2019 Toyota Highlander XLE is the perfect choice. Experience the perfect blend of performance, technology, and luxury. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Highlander XLE should be your next vehicle.

description:
Introducing the 2019 Chevrolet Suburban LT, a powerhouse of a vehicle that combines style, performance, and functionality. This stunning SUV is equipped with an impressive EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, delivering an impressive 355 horsepower and 383 lb-ft of torque. The 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission ensures a smooth and efficient ride, making it the perfect vehicle for both city driving and long road trips.

Step inside and you'll be greeted with a spacious and luxurious interior. The LT trim level offers premium features such as leather seating, heated front seats, and a power sunroof. And with extra spacing, you and your passengers can enjoy a comfortable ride with plenty of legroom and storage space for all your belongings.

But the 2019 Chevrolet Suburban LT is not just about style and comfort. It's also a capable and versatile vehicle, with a maximum towing capacity of up to 8,300 pounds. This makes it the perfect SUV for hauling your boat or trailer on your next adventure.

Safety is always a top priority, and the Suburban LT does not disappoint. It comes equipped with advanced safety features such as forward collision alert, lane keep assist, and rear cross traffic alert to keep you and your loved ones safe on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own the 2019 Chevrolet Suburban LT. Come visit us today and take a test drive to experience the power, comfort, and versatility of this exceptional SUV.

description:
The 2019 Honda CR-V EX is an exceptional choice for those seeking a compact SUV that combines performance, safety, and cutting-edge technology. Powered by a robust 1.5L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, this model delivers a remarkable 190 horsepower and is paired with a continuously variable transmission CVT that ensures a smooth and efficient driving experience.

One of the standout features of the CR-V EX is its commitment to safety. The vehicle is equipped with a forward collision mitigation system that actively monitors the road ahead. This innovative technology helps prevent potential accidents by preparing the vehicle and its occupants for an impending collision. It’s a reassuring feature that adds an extra layer of security during your drives.

In addition to this, the adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go functionality makes long commutes significantly more convenient. This system automatically adjusts your speed to maintain a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, seamlessly bringing you to a stop when traffic halts and resuming pace as it begins to move again. Its an ideal companion for those who spend considerable time on the road.

Another impressive safety feature is the hands-on steering assist/lane centering. This technology helps you stay centered in your lane with minimal effort, while the lane departure prevention system corrects any unintended lane drift, allowing for a worry-free driving experience. Furthermore, the rear camera makes parking and reversing easier by providing enhanced visibility of obstacles behind you.

For the tech-savvy driver, the CR-V EX boasts smart device mirroring, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone with the vehicle’s infotainment system. This feature enhances convenience by enabling you to control your device without diverting your attention from the road. Additionally, the front pedestrian impact prevention system actively scans for pedestrians, taking necessary actions to avoid potential collisions.

In conclusion, the 2019 Honda CR-V EX stands as a top choice for a compact SUV, excelling in performance, safety, and modern technology. With its powerful engine and array of advanced safety features, the CR-V EX is designed to provide a reliable and enjoyable driving experience for urban commutes or weekend getaways alike. Choose the Honda CR-V EX for a vehicle that meets all your driving needs while prioritizing your safety and comfort.

Boasting a commanding 3.6L V6 engine and all-wheel drive, the Traverse High Country delivers a thrilling and confident ride, whether you're navigating city streets or exploring the open road. Designed with your safety in mind, the Traverse High Country comes equipped with a suite of advanced driver assistance features, including Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert. You can drive with confidence, knowing your family is well-protected.

2019 BMW X3 3.0
No Hassle, No Haggle, No games. The price you see is the price you pay!

A perfect balance of luxury, performance, and everyday utility this 2019 BMW X3 3.0 delivers premium German engineering with confident capability and refined comfort. With its smooth inline-6 power, poised handling, and upscale interior, the X3 elevates every drive from daily commutes to weekend getaways.

Key Features & Highlights

3.0-Liter Turbocharged Inline-6 Engine strong, smooth performance with excellent acceleration and highway confidence

8-Speed Automatic Transmission precise shifting for responsive and refined driving

xDrive All-Wheel Drive (if so equipped) enhanced traction and stability in varied road conditions

Premium Interior quality materials and supportive seating for driver and passengers

BMW iDrive Infotainment System intuitive control with crisp display

Apple CarPlay Compatibility seamless smartphone integration

Bluetooth Connectivity hands-free calling and audio streaming

Rearview Camera added confidence when backing up

Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control personalized comfort for front occupants

Alloy Wheels premium design with strong road presence

Why Youll Love It
The 2019 BMW X3 3.0 blends spirited performance with everyday usability. Its powerful yet refined engine and balanced chassis provide engaging driving dynamics, while the upscale interior and modern tech features keep you comfortable and connected. Whether navigating city streets or exploring open roads, this X3 delivers a confident and luxurious ride.

Dealer Notes
Clean, well-maintained, and ready for the road this BMW X3 3.0 offers standout value in the luxury SUV segment. A smart choice for drivers who want premium comfort, performance, and versatility in one sophisticated package.

No Hassle, No Haggle, No games. The price you see is the price you pay!

Once inside our LT, enjoy the Chevrolet MyLink 8-inch diagonal color touchscreen with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, USB ports, Bluetooth, and voice-activated technology. Comfortable heated leather front seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel with mounted audio, cruise controls, available OnStar, and Teen Driver give you all the tools to hit the highway.

Your safety and that of your passengers are imperative. This 2019 Toyota RAV4 LE is a fantastic choice for the savvy car buyer looking for a reliable, feature-packed SUV. With its sleek blue exterior and well-appointed interior, this RAV4 LE delivers an exceptional driving experience.

• One Owner
• Alloy Wheels/Premium Wheels
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Backup Camera/Parking Sensors
• Bluetooth, Hands-Free
• Brake Assist
• Cruise Control
• Keyless Entry
• Premium Sound System/Premium Audio
• Satellite Radio Capable
• Security System
• Stability Control
• Steering Wheel Controls
• USB Port

Under the hood, this RAV4 LE is powered by a potent 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC Dual VVT-i engine, paired with an efficient 8-Speed Automatic transmission and Front-Wheel Drive. With an impressive 26 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway, this SUV delivers exceptional fuel economy without sacrificing performance.

The interior of this RAV4 LE is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the premium sound system, seamless smartphone integration with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and a host of advanced safety features like Backup Camera, Parking Sensors, and Stability Control. The spacious cabin and split-folding rear seats provide ample room for passengers and cargo, making this RAV4 LE the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Backed by Toyota's renowned reputation for reliability and quality, this 2019 RAV4 LE is a smart investment that will provide years of dependable service. Don't miss your chance to experience the exceptional value and features this SUV has to offer.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 Bentley Bentayga V8. This luxurious SUV boasts a commanding presence and unparalleled performance, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this Bentayga V8 is designed to cater to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, the security of a Blind Spot Monitor, and the comfort of Heated Seats and a Heated Steering Wheel. The Backup Camera and Navigation System will ensure you navigate with ease, while the Premium Sound System will immerse you in your favorite music.

• Apple Carplay/Android Auto
• Backup Camera
• Blind Spot Monitor
• Bluetooth
• Heated Seats
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Homelink
• Leather Seats
• Memory Seat
• Navigation System
• Premium Sound System
• Sunroof/Moonroof

Beneath the elegant exterior lies the powerful heart of this Bentayga V8. Equipped with a V8 engine and an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, this SUV delivers an exceptional driving experience, effortlessly navigating the roads with precision and agility. With an impressive fuel efficiency of 15 MPG in the city and 24 MPG on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of performance without sacrificing practicality.

The Bentayga V8's interior is a true sanctuary, crafted with the finest materials and attention to detail. Sink into the luxurious Leather Seats and let the Memory Seat feature adjust the driving position to your exact preferences. The Heated Steering Wheel and Heated Seats will keep you comfortable, no matter the weather, while the Sunroof/Moonroof allows you to bask in the natural light.

Beyond the exceptional features, this Bentayga V8 also boasts an impressive array of advanced safety technologies. From the Dual Front Impact Airbags to the Rear Side Impact Airbag, you can rest assured that you and your passengers are protected. The Electronic Stability Control and Brake Assist further enhance the vehicle's handling and responsiveness, ensuring a secure and confident driving experience.

With its stunning design, uncompromising performance, and exceptional attention to detail, this 2022 Bentley Bentayga V8 is a true masterpiece. Experience the epitome of luxury and power by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident that once you take this remarkable SUV for a spin, you'll be captivated by its unparalleled capabilities and won't want to settle for anything less.

2019 BMW X3 3.0
No Hassle, No Haggle, No games. The price you see is the price you pay!

A perfect balance of luxury, performance, and everyday utility this 2019 BMW X3 3.0 delivers premium German engineering with confident capability and refined comfort. With its smooth inline-6 power, poised handling, and upscale interior, the X3 elevates every drive from daily commutes to weekend getaways.

Key Features & Highlights

3.0-Liter Turbocharged Inline-6 Engine strong, smooth performance with excellent acceleration and highway confidence

8-Speed Automatic Transmission precise shifting for responsive and refined driving

xDrive All-Wheel Drive (if so equipped) enhanced traction and stability in varied road conditions

Premium Interior quality materials and supportive seating for driver and passengers

BMW iDrive Infotainment System intuitive control with crisp display

Apple CarPlay Compatibility seamless smartphone integration

Bluetooth Connectivity hands-free calling and audio streaming

Rearview Camera added confidence when backing up

Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control personalized comfort for front occupants

Alloy Wheels premium design with strong road presence

Why Youll Love It
The 2019 BMW X3 3.0 blends spirited performance with everyday usability. Its powerful yet refined engine and balanced chassis provide engaging driving dynamics, while the upscale interior and modern tech features keep you comfortable and connected. Whether navigating city streets or exploring open roads, this X3 delivers a confident and luxurious ride.

Dealer Notes
Clean, well-maintained, and ready for the road this BMW X3 3.0 offers standout value in the luxury SUV segment. A smart choice for drivers who want premium comfort, performance, and versatility in one sophisticated package.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

Smart design, proven reliability, and modern technology come together in this 2019 Honda CR-V EX AWD, an SUV built to handle daily life with confidence. Finished in sleek Modern Steel Metallic, this 4D Sport Utility offers a refined look backed by dependable performance. Under the hood, the efficient 1.5L I-4 DOHC 16V engine delivers smooth power, while all-wheel drive provides added traction and stability in changing road and weather conditions.

Inside, the CR-V EX offers a spacious and comfortable cabin designed with both driver and passengers in mind. Heated front bucket seats keep you comfortable year-round, while the power moonroof adds an open, airy feel to every drive. Advanced safety features like Blind Spot Information (BSI), Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS), and an exterior rear parking camera help you stay aware and confident on the road. The CR-Vs intuitive layout and generous cargo space make it easy to transition from weekday commuting to weekend adventures.

Riding on stylish 18-inch alloy wheels, this CR-V delivers a smooth, composed ride and excellent fuel efficiency one of the many reasons it remains a top choice among compact SUVs. Its balance of safety, comfort, and long-term dependability makes it an excellent fit for families, professionals, and anyone looking for a versatile, well-equipped vehicle.

You can buy this 2019 Honda CR-V EX AWD today at Ferguson Superstore in Broken Arrow, OK 74012.
At Ferguson, we are Upfront and Simple. We offer our best price to everyone, the first time, so you can enjoy a transparent, stress-free buying experience from start to finish.

2019 Toyota Highlander XLE 4WD — V6, 3.5L, Muskogee OK This 2019 Toyota Highlander XLE delivers dependable performance with a robust 3.5L V6 engine and confident four-wheel drive, perfect for Oklahoma roads and weekend getaways. The XLE trim pairs comfort and technology: enjoy built-in navigation, automatic climate control for personalized comfort, and a back-up camera that simplifies parking and low-speed maneuvers. Safety features include Cross-Traffic Alert to help detect approaching vehicles while reversing and enhance everyday peace of mind. This Toyota Highlander is a CARFAX 1-Owner vehicle, indicating a well-documented history and consistent care. The spacious cabin provides three-row versatility with premium materials and thoughtful storage, ideal for families or those needing flexible cargo space. The refined ride quality and efficient V6 power make it an excellent choice for highway driving and towing light loads. Located in Muskogee, OK, this Toyota Highlander is competitively priced and advertised as the best price in the area, offering exceptional value compared to other pre-owned SUVs. Routine maintenance has been followed per the service records, and the vehicle has been carefully inspected to ensure reliability. If you're searching for a versatile, safe, and comfortable pre-owned SUV with strong resale value, this 2019 Toyota Highlander XLE 4WD with navigation and advanced safety features is worth a test drive in Muskogee. Contact us to schedule a viewing or for more details.

Equipment
The leather seats in this 2019 Toyota Highlander are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. Bluetooth technology is built into this Toyota Highlander, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. You'll never again be lost in a crowded city or a country region with the navigation system on the Toyota Highlander. The vehicle's Cross-Traffic Alert: Safeguarding you from unexpected traffic when reversing. See what's behind you with the back up camera on the Toyota Highlander. The vehicle enhances safety with a blind spot monitor, alerting drivers to potential dangers in adjacent lanes. It offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. This unit has four wheel drive capabilities. This 2019 Toyota Highlander shines with clean polished lines coated with an elegant white finish. Enjoy the convenience of the power liftgate on this model. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in it is easy with the climate control system.

description:
Confident and bold, our 2019 Chevrolet Traverse Premier Redline Edition offered in amazing Mosaic Black Metallic is ready for duty! Powered by a 3.6 Liter V6 that delivers 310hp connected to a 9 Speed Automatic transmission for easy passing. This Front Wheel Drive SUV also scores nearly 27mpg on the highway with easy maneuverability in town and power for towing that toy on the weekends. Our Traverse has a premium look, too, with our package's exclusive red-outlined black badges, a panoramic sunroof, and dark details that include big black alloy wheels, all complemented by LED lighting, fog lamps, a hands-free liftgate, dual exhaust outlets, and heated power mirrors.

Our Premier cabin is engineered for full-size comfort with leather heated/ventilated power front seats, heated second-row captain's chairs, a versatile third row, a heated leather power steering wheel, tri-zone automatic climate control, and upscale technology to help you master every mile. An 8-inch touchscreen is the starting point and supports full-color navigation, Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto®, Bluetooth®, WiFi compatibility, and a 10-speaker Bose sound system.

Chevrolet helps you to avoid and manage challenging driving situations with smart safety measures like a surround-view system, lane-change assistance, blind-spot monitoring, a digital rearview camera, a rear-seat reminder, and more. Our Traverse Premier will more than treat you right! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description:
Discover the epitome of refined capability in this stunning 2019 GMC Yukon XL SLT. This full-size SUV boasts a commanding presence and exceptional versatility, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

• Open Road Package: Includes an additional 9 months of SiriusXM Radio and NavTraffic service, power sunroof, rear seat entertainment system, and premium audio system with navigation.
• Dark Sky Metallic exterior color with Gray interior.

Powered by the robust EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, this Yukon XL delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 15 city/22 highway MPG. The 6-speed automatic transmission with overdrive ensures a smooth and responsive driving experience, while the Rear-Wheel Drive configuration provides confident handling and control.

Step inside and be enveloped in the luxurious cabin, featuring premium leather-appointed seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and a heated steering wheel. The Bose Premium 9-Speaker audio system and SiriusXM Radio provide an immersive entertainment experience for you and your passengers.

Convenience and technology are at your fingertips with features like the Power Tilt-Sliding Sunroof, Power Liftgate, and the IntelliLink infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility. The Enhanced Driver Alert Package, including Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert, provides added peace of mind and safety on the road.

With seating for up to 8 and ample cargo space, this Yukon XL is the perfect choice for families, adventurers, and those who demand a versatile and capable SUV. Experience the uncompromising blend of power, luxury, and utility that this 2019 GMC Yukon XL SLT has to offer.

Oil changes for life @ Seth Wadley Customz

    • Heated steering wheel - A warm touch. Trying to drive with bulky winter gloves on isn't always easy. Keep your hands warm in cold temperatures so you can ditch the mitts and get a firm grip with this heated steering wheel.
    Convenience
    • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
    Safety and Security
    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.

WHY BUY FROM US
Buy with confidence at Group 1 where every used vehicle, up to 175,000 miles, comes with a one month 1,000-mile limited warranty along with a 3-day 250-mile return policy. Some exclusions may apply, see Buyers Guide for specifics. Every vehicle is priced to market and includes a Carfax History Report.

You expect fair & competitive pricing. Thats why the price is based on current market data and is regularly compared to similar pre-owned vehicles in the region.

QUALITY INSPECTIONS
Every vehicle is thoroughly inspected and comes with a complimentary vehicle history report.

QUICK & TRANSPARENT FINANCING

VEHICLE SERVICE CONTRACTS

Current Honda owners love our onsite car service and maintenance center, employing the most Honda Certified Master Technicians in the state that use certified parts from the manufacturer. We make servicing your vehicle a simple, pleasant experience, with complimentary preliminary diagnosis, and over 160 years of combined repair experience. Our friendly management staff has over 60 years of combined Honda experience, most of which at South Pointe Honda, providing transparent pricing on every New, Certified PreOwned and Used vehicle. Our professionial staff is hired for their integrity, respect, professionalism and teamwork. Our entire dealership is here for you to provide the best experience possible, with over 4.5 stars on Carfax, Google, and DealerRater. We look forward to serving you!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and style in the 2019 Subaru Forester Limited. This exceptional SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience with its impressive array of features and advanced technology.

• Popular Package #3, including a Rear Bumper Cover, Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror with Approach Lighting, Dome Light LED Upgrade, Auto-Dimming Mirror with Compass & HomeLink, All-Weather Floor Liners, and a Cargo Net
• Crimson Red Pearl Body Side Molding and Crimson Red Door Edge Guards
• Splash Guards

Powered by a 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT engine and Lineartronic CVT, this Forester Limited delivers a remarkable balance of performance and efficiency, with an impressive 26 MPG in the city and 33 MPG on the highway. Its Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling and traction in all conditions, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

Step inside and experience the refined luxury of the Forester Limited. Sink into the heated, perforated leather-trimmed seats and enjoy the convenience of the STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Plus System, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The panoramic moonroof and dual-zone automatic climate control add to the exceptional comfort, while the power liftgate and Cargo Net make loading and unloading a breeze.

Safety is a top priority in the Forester Limited, with features like Eyesight Driver Assist Technology, Blind-Spot Detection, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a Rear-View Camera keeping you and your loved ones protected. The Certified 7/100K Powertrain Coverage provides added peace of mind, ensuring your investment is well-protected.

With its impressive combination of capability, technology, and style, the 2019 Subaru Forester Limited is a true standout in the crowded SUV market. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the Forester that's perfect for your lifestyle.
