description:
The 2019 INFINITI QX80 Limited 4WD delivers commanding full size SUV performance premium craftsmanship and exceptional capability in a vehicle designed for family travel towing and long distance comfort. With 88250 miles this QX80 reflects consistent responsible use while continuing to offer robust performance supported by proven INFINITI body on frame engineering. Power comes from a powerful 5.6 liter V8 engine paired with a smooth seven speed automatic transmission that provides strong acceleration confident highway cruising and impressive towing capability. The advanced four wheel drive system enhances traction stability and control during rain snow gravel and uneven terrain while maintaining a composed ride on paved roads.

Inside the QX80 Limited offers an upscale spacious cabin crafted with premium materials and attention to detail. Leather appointed seating with quilted accents heated and ventilated front seats heated second row seats and a power adjustable driver seat with memory create a first class driving environment. The wide cabin layout provides generous headroom and legroom across all three rows making it ideal for families passengers and extended travel. Second and third row seats fold flat to expand cargo capacity for luggage sports equipment or hauling needs. Rich trim accents ambient interior lighting and excellent sound insulation elevate the overall cabin experience.

Technology in the 2019 QX80 Limited is advanced intuitive and driver focused. A large color touchscreen anchors the INFINITI infotainment system with navigation Apple CarPlay Android Auto Bluetooth and voice command capability. Rear seat entertainment keeps passengers engaged on long drives while a premium Bose audio system delivers rich sound throughout the cabin. A surround view camera system provides a 360 degree perspective for easier parking maneuvering and trailer alignment. Keyless entry push button start remote engine start multiple USB ports and a digital driver information display add everyday convenience.

Safety remains a core strength of the QX80 lineup. This Limited trim includes automatic emergency braking blind spot warning rear cross traffic alert lane departure warning intelligent cruise control and parking sensors. Stability control traction control antilock braking and a comprehensive airbag system support confident driving across a wide range of conditions. The elevated driving position improves outward visibility while the solid frame construction contributes to durability towing confidence and occupant protection.

The exterior of the 2019 INFINITI QX80 Limited 4WD features bold luxury styling with LED lighting premium alloy wheels chrome accents roof rails and INFINITI signature grille. Its commanding stance delivers a strong upscale road presence suitable for professional personal and family use. The combination of V8 power true four wheel drive premium interior features advanced technology and proven reliability makes this QX80 Limited an outstanding option for drivers seeking a value driven luxury full size SUV with serious capability.

Why Buy from Jackie Cooper Nissan
Every used vehicle on our lot goes through a strenuous 150 point inspection before it is ever offered for sale because quality and safety are part of our heritage. Our factory trained technicians examine all major systems including the engine transmission brakes suspension tires and electrical components to ensure each vehicle meets our high standards for performance and reliability. We also inspect for signs of prior damage mechanical issues and cosmetic wear inside and out. If something does not meet our strict criteria it is either repaired or replaced before the vehicle reaches the lot. This careful process reflects our commitment to your peace of mind because you deserve a vehicle you can count on.

Discover the ultimate in luxury and performance with this stunning 2019 GMC Yukon SLT. This exceptional SUV is a true testament to GMC's commitment to excellence, offering a commanding presence on the road and a wealth of premium features to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting an impressive list of upgrades, this Yukon SLT is equipped with the following:

• Open Road Package, including additional 9 months of SiriusXM Radio and NavTraffic service, power sunroof, rear seat entertainment system, and premium audio system with navigation
• 20" Polished Aluminum Wheels
• Power Release Second-Row Bucket Seats
• White Frost Tricoat Exterior

Step inside and be greeted by the Yukon's spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium leather-appointed seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and a Bose premium audio system to elevate your listening experience. The power-adjustable pedals and steering column ensure a personalized fit, while the hands-free power programmable rear liftgate and push-button keyless start add to the convenience.

Safety and technology are also at the forefront, with features like Forward Collision Alert, Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, and the intuitive IntelliLink infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The Yukon's impressive towing capacity and powerful EcoTec3 V8 engine make it a versatile choice for your adventurous lifestyle, whether you're hauling the family or towing your toys.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and versatility with this exceptional 2019 Volkswagen Tiguan 2.0T SEL Premium 4Motion. This sophisticated SUV offers a commanding presence on the road, coupled with a refined and well-appointed interior that will elevate your driving experience.

• Navigation System
• 8 Speakers
• SiriusXM Radio
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Power Liftgate
• Panoramic Sunroof
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Leather Seating Surfaces

Boasting a 2.0L turbocharged engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission with Tiptronic, this Tiguan delivers a seamless blend of power and efficiency, with an impressive EPA-estimated 21 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway. The advanced 4Motion all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling and traction, no matter the road conditions.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium Vienna Leather seating, a heated steering wheel, and a suite of advanced technology features. The Discover Media infotainment system, with its intuitive touchscreen interface, provides easy access to navigation, audio, and connectivity options, keeping you connected and entertained on every journey.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Forward Collision Warning, Autonomous Emergency Braking, and Blind Spot Monitoring working tirelessly to help protect you and your passengers. The Tiguan's impressive list of standard and available safety technologies provides the peace of mind you deserve.

Whether you're tackling your daily commute or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2019 Volkswagen Tiguan 2.0T SEL Premium 4Motion is the perfect companion. Its blend of style, performance, and advanced features make it a standout choice in the competitive SUV market.

We invite you to experience the exceptional quality and craftsmanship of this Tiguan for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

Serving drivers near Denver, Aurora, Littleton, Lakewood, Boulder, and surrounding Colorado areas.

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2019 Honda Passport Sport. Boasting a sleek blue exterior and a well-appointed interior, this versatile SUV is ready to take on your daily adventures and weekend getaways with ease.

Highlighted features include:
- 215-Watt Audio System with 7 Speakers
- Back-Up Camera
- 2 LCD Monitors In The Front
- Radio with Seek-Scan, Clock, Steering Wheel Controls and Voice Activation
- Automatic Temperature Control
- Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
- Traction Control
- Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS) + FCW Mitigation
- Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS)
- Rear Parking Camera

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 engine and equipped with All-Wheel Drive, this Passport Sport delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 mpg in the city and 24 mpg on the highway. Whether you're navigating the urban jungle or exploring the great outdoors, this Honda SUV is up for the challenge.

The spacious and well-appointed interior of the Passport Sport offers ample room for you and your passengers to stretch out and enjoy the ride. Thoughtful features like dual-zone automatic climate control, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a premium audio system ensure your comfort and convenience.

Safety is also a top priority, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Collision Mitigation Braking System, Lane Keeping Assist, and a Rear-View Camera, providing you with added peace of mind on the road.

This 2019 Honda Passport Sport is an exceptional value, priced at just $20,000. With its impressive capabilities, sophisticated design, and well-equipped interior, it's an SUV that truly stands out in its class. We invite you to experience the difference for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this Passport Sport can elevate your driving experience.

description: *2019 Toyota RAV4 Hybrid Limited AWD -- Clean CARFAX*Earnhardt Toyota of Mesa is pleased to offer you this 2019 Toyota RAV4 Hybrid Limited AWD finished in elegant Blizzard Pearl with a refined Nutmeg SofTex®-trimmed interior and showing 50,686 miles. This upscale hybrid SUV blends impressive fuel efficiency, advanced technology, and Toyota's renowned reliability, making it an excellent choice for drivers who want comfort, capability, and long-term value.Powered by a 2.5L 4-cylinder hybrid engine paired with an electronically controlled CVT and all-wheel drive, this RAV4 Hybrid delivers smooth, confident performance along with exceptional efficiency. It offers an EPA-estimated 41 MPG city and 38 MPG highway, making it ideal for commuting, road trips, and reducing fuel costs without sacrificing versatility.Inside, the Nutmeg SofTex® interior creates a warm and premium cabin environment with thoughtful design and modern technology throughout. Features include a panoramic glass roof, advanced navigation with premium audio, dual-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable front seating, and intuitive infotainment that keeps everything easily within reach. The interior layout is both comfortable and functional, offering flexibility for passengers and cargo alike.Safety and driver-assist technology are seamlessly integrated, including blind spot monitoring, lane tracing assist, adaptive cruise control, pre-collision systems, stability and traction control, and a comprehensive airbag system to support confidence on every drive.The Blizzard Pearl exterior presents a clean, sophisticated appearance with sleek body lines, LED lighting accents, and timeless RAV4 styling that continues to stand out on the road.*Earnhardt Toyota of Mesa**6136 E Auto Loop Ave, Mesa, AZ 85206**480-807-9700*

description: Celestial Silver Metallic 2019 Toyota Highlander XLE AWD ?' One Owner ?' Scottsdale, AZ Spacious, refined, and built for family comfort, this 2019 Toyota Highlander XLE AWD in elegant Celestial Silver Metallic delivers strong performance and premium features in a versatile midsize SUV. Powered by a smooth and capable 3.5L V6 engine, the Highlander offers confident acceleration along with the added traction of All-Wheel Drive, ideal for road trips and everyday driving around Scottsdale, Phoenix, Mesa, and Tempe. This vehicle is a CARFAX One-Owner with a Clean CARFAX Vehicle History Report, offering added confidence in your purchase. Inside, the Highlander XLE blends comfort and technology with upscale finishes and family-friendly space. Key Features All-Wheel Drive capability Leather Seat Trim Heated Front Bucket Seats Power Moonroof Power Liftgate Navigation System Active Cruise Control Front Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control Alloy Wheels Heated Door Mirrors Remote Keyless Entry Safety and stability features such as Electronic Stability Control, Traction Control, ABS brakes, and a Tire Pressure Monitoring System help provide peace of mind on every drive. Every pre-owned vehicle we offer undergoes a detailed 145-point inspection to help ensure safety, reliability, and overall quality before it reaches our lot. Conveniently located in Scottsdale, we proudly serve drivers from Phoenix, Glendale, Avondale, Sun City, Cave Creek, Mesa, and Tempe. If you are searching for a used Toyota Highlander AWD near Phoenix with leather, navigation, and family-ready comfort, this XLE model is an excellent choice. Come see why the Toyota Highlander remains one of the most trusted midsize SUVs on the road.

This Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat 2019 Jeep Grand Cherokee Trailhawk would be a welcomed addition to your family/business. This Grand Cherokee has the following options: ENGINE: 3.6L V6 24V VVT UPG I W/ESS, TRANSMISSION: 8-SPEED AUTOMATIC (850RE), QUICK ORDER PACKAGE 2BJ, 3.45 REAR AXLE RATIO, GRANITE CRYSTAL METALLIC CLEARCOAT, RUBY RED/BLACK, TRAILHAWK LEATHER TRIM SEATS W/PERFORATION, GVWR: 6,500 LBS, TRAILHAWK LUXURY GROUP, FULL SIZE SPARE TIRE, FRONT LICENSE PLATE BRACKET, MANUFACTURER'S STATEMENT OF ORIGIN This Grand Cherokee has the following features: Trailhawk Luxury Group ($2,995 value)
  • Trailhawk Leather Trim Seats
  • Cargo Compartment Cover
  • Dual-Pane Panoramic Sunroof
  • Rain Sensitive Windshield Wipers
  • Bi-Xenon HID Headlamps
  • Auto High Beam Headlamp Control
  • LED Daytime Running Headlamps
  • Front LED Fog Lamps
  • Power Tilt/telescope Steering Column
Quick Order Package 2BJ
    Comfort
    • Ventilated front seats -That's cool. Ventilated front seats provides targeted cool air so you and your passenger can get comfortable quicker in hot weather. Getting comfortable is no sweat when you have ventilated front seats.
    Convenience
    • Smart device and keyfob engine start control - Phone ahead. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob or your smart device, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, ,thanks to Smart device and Keyfob engine start control.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.
    To be sure you don't miss out, why not call us at 928-774-5337 and schedule a test drive. We are located at 5190 N Test Drive Flagstaff AZ 86004. We look forward to seeing you soon.

ADAPTIVE CRUISE CONTROL!! BLIND SPOT MONITOR!! CROSS-TRAFFIC ALERT!! REAR PARKING AID!! THIRD ROW SEATING!! POWER SEAT!! INTELLIGENT KEY!! REMOTE ENGINE START SYSTEM!! PREMIUM 8" COLOR DISPLAY!! REAR VIEW MONITOR!! PREMIUM FACTORY ALLOY WHEELS!! TOW PACKAGE!! A REALLY NICE PATHFINDER!! Goldie's Motors has implemented a new transparent and aggressive pricing structure. To be competitive and give our customers the best possible value. We are pricing select vehicles at or below our cost. We only charge a $385.00 doc fee plus an additional $1,000 on top of the sale price, which is the majority of our total profit on the car. Our fees will include a complete vehicle inspection, window tinting, floor mats, and a complete detail. There are absolutely no hidden costs or miscellaneous fees. Our total vehicle costs will be hard to beat! In addition, we will not sacrifice the quality of our vehicles and continue to go through each car thoroughly. We aim to increase our volume and offer our customers the best possible experience. We are a family-owned store. Both of our owners (brothers) are based in Arizona. The store is staffed with residents, veterans, and retirees, and we all contribute to the success of our community. Our kids go to the local schools, we donate to local charities, and we volunteer throughout our communities. We would appreciate the opportunity to earn your business. We just got this sharp and very well-cared-for upgraded Pathfinder from a very trusted national lender. The last owner took really nice care of this Nissan. It has a fantastic 58,281 miles, that is only an average of 8,325 miles driven per year!! When we purchased this Pathfinder it was announced as structural alteration due to the towing package. It is really nice!! The very sharp and upgraded magnetic black exterior paint looks great and is in excellent condition especially for its year and the miles. The equally sharp premium interior is equally nice and has been well-maintained, there is no sign it has been smoked in. This is very well equipped with all the options listed above, plus a long, long list of factory upgrades that make it a very, very nice upgraded luxury and high performance suv that looks and drives great — and the overall condition reflects how well it’s been cared for. In addition it has just been fully serviced by our Nissan specialist, including a comprehensive multi-point pre-owned vehicle inspection, and everything checked out in excellent condition. Since this is a Carfax-certified vehicle with an excellent service history and a fully completed pre-owned inspection, it qualifies for several certified pre-owned (CPO) extended warranty options at reduced rates. Our family environment and great pricing not only make Goldie’s Motors one of the most comfortable places to buy a car, but it also makes us one of the FASTEST. You can drive out of our dealership in less than an hour after selecting your future car! WE ARE OPEN 6 DAYS A WEEK. Please visit us Monday-Friday, 8:30 am-6 pm, and Saturday, 8:30 am-4 pm, or call to schedule an appointment at our all-new Sales and Service center in Mesa, Arizona. We strive to offer a better customer experience, so please check out our website at www.goldiesmotors.com and our thousands of reviews on Google.com, Cars.com, BBB of Arizona, and others! For a free copy of the CARFAX, don't hesitate to get in touch with us by phone or email at sales@goldiesmotors.com *At Goldie’s Motors, we do our best to verify all the options on our vehicles, but due to the auto-population on part of our advertisement we cannot guarantee all the options are correct. part of our advertisement, we cannot guarantee all the options

Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort and technology. The panoramic roof floods the interior with natural light, enhancing the spacious feel. Enjoy the convenience of a hands-free liftgate and keyless entry, while the leather steering wheel and power-adjustable seats with lumbar support provide a tailored driving experience. Stay connected with smart device integration and satellite radio, all controlled effortlessly via steering wheel audio controls. Safety is paramount, with features like Front Collision Mitigation, Driver Monitoring, and Automatic Highbeams ensuring peace of mind on every journey. The X3 M40i is not just a vehicle it s an invitation to explore, designed for those who demand more from their drive. Be sure to call or visit Camelback Hyundai Kia to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description: Experience the 2019 GMC Terrain SLT: A Perfect Blend of Style, Comfort, and Advanced Technology for the Modern Driver Step into the world of refined driving with the 2019 GMC Terrain SLT, where style meets functionality. This Quicksilver Metallic beauty is designed for those who appreciate sophistication and performance. The turbocharged 1.5L DOHC engine, paired with a 9-speed automatic transmission, ensures a smooth and responsive drive, whether you re navigating city streets or embarking on a weekend getaway. Safety is paramount, with features like Automatic Headlights, Integrated Turn Signal Mirrors, and a comprehensive airbag system providing peace of mind on every journey. The Terrain SLT s advanced technology suite includes a Back-Up Camera, Bluetooth Connection, and Smart Device Integration, keeping you connected and in control. Indulge in comfort with heated leather seats and a power driver seat, ensuring every ride is as enjoyable as the destination. The Multi-Zone Climate Control and Auto-Dimming Rearview Mirror add to the luxurious experience, while the Remote Engine Start and Keyless Entry offer convenience at your fingertips. With its striking design and cutting-edge features, the 2019 GMC Terrain SLT is not just a vehicle it s your partner in adventure, ready to take on whatever the road ahead holds. Be sure to call or visit Camelback Ford Lincoln to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

Introducing the stunning and powerful 2019 Mercedes-Benz GLC GLC 300 4MATIC. This luxury SUV combines style, performance, and technology, making it the ultimate choice for those seeking a premium driving experience.

Step inside the spacious and modern cabin, where you will be greeted with premium leather seats, elegant wood trim, and advanced technology at your fingertips. The GLC 300 4MATIC is equipped with a 10.25-inch touchscreen display, allowing you to effortlessly control features such as navigation, music, and climate control.

Under the hood, you will find a turbocharged 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine, delivering an impressive 255 horsepower and 273 lb-ft of torque. The 4MATIC all-wheel-drive system ensures that you have optimal traction and control in all road conditions.

Safety is a top priority in the GLC 300 4MATIC, with features such as active brake assist, blind spot assist, and lane keeping assist to help prevent accidents and keep you and your passengers safe.

With its sleek design, powerful engine, and advanced features, the 2019 Mercedes-Benz GLC GLC 300 4MATIC is the perfect combination of luxury and performance. Come test drive one today and experience the ultimate in driving excellence.

Experience rugged elegance with the 2019 Jeep Compass Trailhawk 4x4, a vehicle that combines off-road prowess with sophisticated style. This particular model boasts a striking White Clearcoat exterior, which contrasts beautifully with its vibrant Ruby Red and Black leather interior. Under the hood, you'll find a capable 2.4L 4-cylinder engine, perfectly paired with a Four Wheel Drive drivetrain that conquers any terrain effortlessly.Designed for both adventurers and comfort seekers, this Trailhawk edition is enriched with a suite of premium features. The pano sunroof and power front/fixed rear full sunroof invite the outdoors in, while the remote start ensures your Compass is ready to go when you are. Inside, heated leather seats provide warmth and luxury, and a Leather Interior Group adds an extra touch of refinement. Drivers also benefit from modern conveniences like Bluetooth connectivity, a blind spot monitor, and parking assist, making every journey both safe and enjoyable.Further enhancing its appeal, the Compass Trailhawk is equipped with a Safety & Security Group to ensure peace of mind on the road. Smart features such as rain-sensing wipers and a power liftgate add to the vehicle's practicality and ease of use. A moonroof adds an extra dimension of openness to the cabin, and the distinctive Black Clearcoat accents highlight its adventurous spirit. Whether navigating city streets or exploring off the beaten path, the 2019 Jeep Compass Trailhawk 4x4 delivers a driving experience that caters to the most discerning of drivers. Advanced Safety Systems, Luxury And Low Miles! Navigation System And Perforated Leather-Trimmed Upholstery! Power Moonroof: Panoramic! Stay Connected With Apple Carplay And Android Auto! Dual-function X-MODE with Hill Descent Control! CARFAX One-Owner! Clean CARFAX! Tucson Subaru is offering for sale this Crystal White Pearl 2019 Subaru Forester Touring AWD Lineartronic CVT 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC! Expertly Capable! This Forester Touring lets nothing get in the way of an out-of-the-way place. With 8.7 inches of ground clearance and standard Subaru Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, you'll take on different driving conditions with confidence. And you can count on the direct-injection SUBARU BOXER engine for increased power without sacrificing fuel economy. If the road changes, standard SI-DRIVE allows you to maximize control. For even tougher roads, the dual-function X-MODE with Hill Descent Control includes two specifically engineered settings: one for snow and dirt, one for deep snow and mud! Come See This Low Mile Gem Today!

GPS Navigation System, Perforated Leather-Trimmed Upholstery, Driver's Memory seat, Power Liftgate, Power Moonroof/Sunroof: Panoramic! From The Wheels That Slip To The Wheels That Grip! SYMMETRICAL ALL-WHEEL DRIVE! Radio: Subaru Starlink 8.0" Multimedia Nav System, Harman Kardon 576W Amp & Speaker System, CD player, USB port, Bluetooth Wireless, STARLINK/Apple CarPlay/Android Auto and Steering wheel mounted audio controls! EyeSight is an extra set of eyes on the road, and if need be, an extra foot on the brake when you drive! EyeSight Driver Assist Technology is Adaptive Cruise Control, Pre-Collision Throttle Management, Pre-Collision Braking, Lane Departure and Sway Warning with Lane Keep Assist! Reverse Automatic Braking, Blind-Spot Detection with Lane Change Assist and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert! DriverFocus Distraction Mitigation System, Engineered for both new and experienced drivers, it works together with Subaru EyeSight to help detect distracted or drowsy driving. If the drivers attention strays from the road for too long, DriverFocus can deliver visual and auditory alerts to bring attention back to the road, its like having an attentive co-pilot along for the ride! X-MODE optimizes engine output and transmission ratio, increases all-wheel drive system engagement and uses enhanced control of the VDC system to reduce or increase individual wheelspin, providing optimal traction on various types of terrain and low friction surfaces! Alloy wheels, Exterior Parking Camera Rear, Front dual zone A/C, Heated Front Bucket Seats, Speed control,Keyless Access with Push-Button Start and More!

With an original MSRP of $47,545, this 2019 BMW X3 offers a well-balanced combination of luxury, performance, and everyday practicality in a compact luxury SUV. Designed with BMWs signature driving dynamics, the X3 delivers a refined yet engaging experience for both city driving and longer trips.

Equipped with the Navigation Package, a $1,700 factory upgrade, this X3 features enhanced route guidance and infotainment functionality, while the panoramic moonroof, a $1,350 option, fills the cabin with natural light and an open, airy feel. The XLine trim adds distinctive styling elements, complemented by satin aluminum exterior trim and 18-inch wheels that create a sophisticated and rugged appearance.

Inside, comfort and convenience are prioritized with heated front seats and Park Distance Control to assist with low-speed maneuvering and parking. Technology highlights include a 12-speaker sound system for clear, immersive audio, Apple CarPlay integration for seamless smartphone connectivity, and a rearview camera for added confidence. Combining premium features, versatile design, and BMW performance, this 2019 BMW X3 stands out as a smart and well-equipped luxury SUV.

Rigorously Inspected & Serviced
While this vehicle is not part of our Allstate Signature Certified due to the model year, it has undergone a thorough inspection and professional servicing to meet our high-quality standards

The CBB Advantage: Your vehicle has been enhanced with the CBB Advantage Package, which includes: Premium Ceramic Paint Coating. Ceramic Window Tint. Applied immediately after our expert detailing process when the paint surface is at its cleanest these upgrades provide long-lasting protection, easier cleaning, and a showroom finish.

While these enhancements typically cost $3,000+ at specialty shops, you'll enjoy them for just $998 that will be added to the sales price. Ask a CBB Product Specialist about the many other benefits of the CBB Advantage.

This 2019 Kia Sportage EX is a remarkable SUV that combines style, performance, and unparalleled value. Outfitted with the EX Sport Appearance Package, this Sportage boasts a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that caters to your every need. The cool gray color scheme and premium leather seating create a refined and sophisticated ambiance. Heated front seats and a heated steering wheel ensure your comfort, no matter the weather. The Kia's advanced technology features, including Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, seamlessly integrate your smartphone for a truly connected driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like forward collision warning, lane keep assist, and a rear-view camera keeping you and your loved ones protected. The Sportage's impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 22 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway, means you can enjoy the ride without constantly worrying about the gas pump.

description:
Advanced Safety Systems! Power moonroof: Panoramic! Blind Spot Detection with Rear Cross Traffic Alert + Reverse Automatic Braking + Multimedia Plus Audio + Harman Kardon Amplifier and Speakers + Power Rear Gate! Stay Connected With Apple Carplay And Android Auto! From The Wheels That Slip To The Wheels That Grip! Tucson Subaru is offering for sale this Crystal White Pearl 2019 Subaru Forester Sport AWD Lineartronic CVT 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT. Its hard to miss the distinctive styling of the 2019Forester Sport with it's Orange and gloss black accents characterize its unique interior and exterior, while 18-inch alloy wheels help to make its presence known. Step in, and you'll notice its LED interior lighting, including an exclusive rear gate light. And once you get going, its abilities will immediately become apparent. This Forester Sport easily meets the demands of the drive with the enhanced SI-DRIVE system. And with the dual-function X-MODE feature, it can take on tough conditions and challenging terrain. Wherever the road takes you, roof rail tie-down points keep your cargo tight and secure! Come see it TODAY!

Power moonroof/sunroof! Heated front bucket seats and a power driver seat! Radio: Subaru Starlink 8.0" Multimedia Plus System with Harman Kardon 576W Amp & Speaker System, STARLINK/Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Bluetooth Wireless, CD player and Steering wheel mounted audio controls! SYMMETRICAL ALL-WHEEL DRIVE! EyeSight is an extra set of eyes on the road, and if need be, an extra foot on the brake when you drive! EyeSight Driver Assist Technology is Adaptive Cruise Control, Pre-Collision Throttle Management, Pre-Collision Braking, Lane Departure and Sway Warning!Using radar sensors, Blind-Spot Detection warns you with a visual indicator on your exterior mirror if the system detects a vehicle in your blind spot. Another feature of this system, Lane Change Assist, alerts you with a flashing indicator on your exterior mirror if it senses a vehicle approaching at a higher speed in a a neighboring lane and you signal for a lane change. Rear Cross-Traffic Alert uses radar sensors to help warn you of traffic approaching from the side as you are backing up, utilizing a flashing visual indicator on your exterior mirror and Rear-Vision Camera display as well as an audible warning. Reverse Automatic Braking can detect objects directly behind your vehicle when backing up at a low speed and can help bring the Forester to a stop if it detects an object within its range and the brakes have yet to be applied! Keyless Access with Push-Button Start, Exterior Parking Camera Rear, Power Rear Gate, Reverse Automatic Braking System (RAB), Speed control and MORE!


Expect a relaxed, family-centered atmosphere that is committed to your satisfaction when you visit Tucson Subaru. Our Sales Team is the most knowledgeable, personable, and enjoyable in the industry. We listen to your needs and treat our customers with respect and appreciation in a honest and straightforward manner. Tucson Subaru offers a dedicated Internet Sales Department that allows you the ability to select your vehicle, negotiate a competitive price, and arrange for aggressive financing or lease alternatives - all in a friendly, hassle-free environment without ever leaving the comfort of your home or office. We promise the easiest car purchase you have ever made.

I-10 Automotive Group has been recognized in 2023 and 2024 as the "Best Used Car Dealer in Chandler." We offer transparent service history through Carfax.com and a sales process that is simple and easy to follow. Our new location, located on 881 S Country Club Dr. in Gilbert, AZ, is a renovated state-of-the-art facility with comfortable amenities and quick access to great food and fuel on your way home. Our transparent pre-owned vehicles come with a Carfax report. The Carfax vehicle history report is based only on the information supplied to Carfax and may not include all information or be up to date. I-10 Automotive Group does not warrant the claims made by Carfax to be accurate or up to date. We recommend that you use the Carfax report as an important guide, together with a vehicle inspection as well as a test drive, to help you make a better decision as to the vehicle's condition. Each vehicle is backed by a 15-day/500 mile limited drivetrain warranty. Our cars receive a special I-10 Automotive Group Premium package, which includes a ceramic coating applied at detail that is backed by a 3yr/unlimited mile warranty, free tint redeemable for 30 days, a free oil change, and a $500 spiff for sending a customer to us that purchases a vehicle. description: Explore the Road Ahead with the 2019 Volkswagen Atlas 3.6L V6 SE w/Technology: A Pure White Masterpiece for the Modern Adventurer Step into the world of sophistication and capability with the 2019 Volkswagen Atlas 3.6L V6 SE w/Technology. This Pure White SUV is tailored for those who seek both style and substance in their driving experience. With a robust V6 engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Atlas promises a smooth and powerful ride, perfect for navigating city streets or embarking on weekend getaways. Safety is paramount, and this Atlas doesn t compromise. Equipped with advanced features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Departure Warning, and Front Collision Mitigation, you can drive with confidence knowing you re protected from every angle. The Adaptive Cruise Control and Lane Keeping Assist ensure a stress-free journey, whether you re on a long highway drive or maneuvering through urban traffic. Inside, the Atlas offers a spacious and versatile interior with a 3rd-row seat, accommodating your family and friends comfortably. The heated front seats and premium synthetic upholstery add a touch of luxury, while the smart device integration keeps you connected on the go. With its power liftgate and remote engine start, convenience is at your fingertips. The 2019 Volkswagen Atlas is more than just a vehicle it s your partner in adventure. Be sure to call or visit Peoria Ford to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2019 Chevrolet Equinox Premier. This meticulously maintained SUV boasts a stunning Blue exterior and a wealth of premium features that will captivate the discerning buyer.

Highlights of this Equinox Premier include:
• Confidence & Convenience II Package
• Infotainment II Package
• Interior Protection Package (LPO)
• Front & Rear Black Bowtie Emblems (LPO)
• Universal Tablet Holders (LPO)
• Bose Premium 7-Speaker Audio System
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Power Liftgate
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Forward Collision Alert
• Lane Keep Assist with Lane Departure Warning

Powered by a 1.5L DOHC engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Equinox Premier delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 26 city/32 highway MPG.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium leather-appointed seating, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a state-of-the-art Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium system with connected navigation and a Bose premium audio system. The Equinox Premier also boasts a wealth of advanced safety features, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Forward Collision Alert, and Lane Keep Assist, providing you and your loved ones with added peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2019 Chevrolet Equinox Premier is the perfect companion. With its exceptional combination of style, technology, and performance, it's a vehicle that will elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations. We invite you to schedule a test drive and discover the true potential of this remarkable SUV.

• Local Trade

Boasting a striking white exterior and a well-appointed interior, this Rogue SL is a true head-turner. Under the hood, the 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine delivers a smooth and efficient ride, with an impressive 26 city/33 highway MPG rating.

Slip into the luxurious leather-appointed seats and experience the comfort of the Quick Comfort Heated Front Bucket Seats. The power driver's seat and memory function allow you to find your perfect driving position with ease. Stay connected with the advanced NissanConnect infotainment system, featuring a navigation system, SiriusXM radio, and a premium 9-speaker audio setup.

Safety is a top priority, and this Rogue SL is equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Enjoy the peace of mind provided by features like Blind Spot Warning, Automatic High-Beam Headlights, and the Emergency Communication System.

Versatility is key in an SUV, and the Rogue SL delivers. The Power Liftgate and 60/40 split-folding rear seats make loading and unloading a breeze, while the Retractable Cargo Cover provides added security for your belongings.

This well-maintained Rogue SL is a true gem, and it's waiting for you to experience its exceptional blend of style, technology, and capability. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this vehicle is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

Discover the ultimate off-road companion in this exceptional 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara. Boasting a rugged 3.6L V6 engine, 4-wheel drive capabilities, and a commanding presence, this Wrangler is ready to take on any adventure you have in mind.

Highlighted features include:
• Heated Seats
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Remote Start
• SiriusXM Ready
• Cruise Control
• Black 3-Piece Hard Top
• AM/FM Radio

Elevate your driving experience with the 5-speed automatic transmission, Black 3-Piece Hard Top, and Remote Start System. Stay connected with the SiriusXM-ready radio, while the Heated Front Seats ensure maximum comfort, no matter the weather.

This Wrangler's versatility is unmatched, with the ability to seamlessly transition from the daily commute to off-road exploration. The powerful 4WD system and Heavy Duty Suspension provide the confidence and capability to tackle any terrain, while the Rear Window Defroster and Wiper/Washer keep you moving forward in any conditions.

Thoughtful touches, such as the Freedom Panel Storage Bag and Cloth Seats with Adjustable Head Restraints, showcase the Wrangler's commitment to functionality and comfort. The Jeep's iconic style is enhanced by the Body Color Appliques on the Front and Rear Bumpers, as well as the Body Color/Accent Color Grille.

Priced at $22,934, this 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is an exceptional value, offering unparalleled capability, comfort, and style. Price does not include $998 Documentation Fee. Price excludes applicable tax, tag, and fees. Price may not include dealer installed accessories.

description: $0 DOWN ON APPROVED CREDIT AS PRICED COMES WITH 3 MONTH UNLIM MILE SERVICE CONTRACT MANAGERS NOTES - HEATED LEATHER, REARVIEW CAMERA, CROSS-TRAFFIC ALERT, TRACTION CONTROL, 12 SPEAKER SOUND SYSTEM, APPLE CARPLAY/ ANDROID AUTO 2017 Ford Expedition Platinum – Overview & Features The 2017 Ford Expedition in Platinum trim represents the top of the lineup for Ford’s full-size SUV, combining powerful performance, a spacious and upscale interior, and plenty of tech and comfort features. It’s built for families, towing, and long-distance drives, offering strong capability and premium amenities that justify its flagship status. Performance & Capability Engine & Transmission: At its heart is a 3.5-liter EcoBoost® twin-turbo V6 engine, producing strong power and torque suited for hauling passengers and trailers alike. This engine is paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission that includes manual shift capability for more control when needed. Towing & Driving: The Platinum trim benefits from robust capability, including an available four-wheel drive and adaptive suspension options that enhance ride comfort and handling. Maximum towing capacity approaches 9,200 pounds when properly equipped — making it practical for boats, campers, and heavy loads. Exterior Highlights Bold Full-Size SUV Presence: The Platinum wears a commanding road presence with large body proportions, chrome exterior accents, and standard 22-inch polished aluminum wheels that distinguish it from lower trims. Premium Lighting & Glass: Features like LED lighting, privacy glass, and available rain-sensing wipers add convenience and aesthetic appeal. Sunroof & Roof Features: A power sunroof or panoramic glass roof is commonly included, letting light into the cabin and adding to the upscale touch. Interior Comfort & Design Seating & Space: The Platinum is designed to seat up to eight passengers with generous headroom and legroom for all three rows. Premium leather upholstery and luxury seating surfaces enhance comfort, while heated and power-adjustable front seats come standard. Materials & Ambience: Expect high-quality interior materials with woodgrain or accent trim, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and thoughtful touches throughout the cabin that project refinement suited to its flagship status. Cargo & Versatility: Third-row seating can fold down to expand cargo space, and power-folding third-row options make reconfiguring the interior easier for gear or luggage. Technology & Connectivity Infotainment: The Platinum trim typically includes Ford’s SYNC® 3 infotainment system with an 8-inch touchscreen, voice-activated navigation, and seamless integration for Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto™. Audio Excellence: A premium Sony® audio system with 12 speakers and subwoofer brings an immersive listening experience to long journeys. Convenience Features: Standard tech features often include push-button start, multiple USB/12V outlets, rear entertainment options, Bluetooth® connectivity, and hands-free phone integration. Safety & Driver Assistance Suite of Safety Gear: Standard safety features include a rearview camera, stability and traction control systems, blind-spot monitoring with cross-traffic alert, and multiple airbags for passenger protection. Fiability Ratings: Independent testing shows the 2017 Expedition lineup, including Platinum, with strong safety scores from agencies like NHTSA, making it a solid choice for family travel.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: The most acclaimed SUV, our 2017 Cadillac Escalade ESV Premium Luxury AWD is vibrant in Crystal White Tricoat! Powered by a massive 6.2 Liter V8 that generates 420hp connected to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission. This All Wheel Drive SUV helps you enjoy nearly 21mpg on the highway and a capable, poised ride thanks partly to selectable Magnetic Ride Control suspension. Our Escalade ESV Premium Luxury boasts gorgeous alloy wheels, a sunroof, a hands-free liftgate, and an overall strong presence that can't be ignored.The masterfully crafted Premium Luxury cabin can accommodate up to 8 people and indulges you with adaptive remote start, leather, a heated steering wheel, heated second-row seats, heated/cooled front seats, and tri-zone automatic climate control. Our CUE and media touchscreen with embedded navigation will guide you to your destination while you stay safely connected via Bluetooth® and OnStar with WiFi capability. Entertainment is at your fingertips with premium Bose audio with HD/satellite radio and a rear Blu-Ray player with two overhead-mounted displays.Advanced safety features from Cadillac, such as a surround-view camera, a head-up display, automatic park assist, blind spot monitoring, lane departure warning, forward collision warning, and adaptive cruise control, add to the confidence you'll feel each time you get behind the wheel. The pinnacle of luxury and refinement paired with incredible capability, our Escalade ESV Premium Luxury is a wise choice. Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! Why Buy from Spartanburg Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram? When you choose this 2017 BMW X3 sDrive28i from Spartanburg Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram, you're not just buying a used car - you're investing in quality, reliability, and peace of mind. Located in Spartanburg SC, we're proud to offer the best selection of certified pre-owned BMWvehicles and top-tier used cars in our local market. This 2017 BMW X3 sDrive28i, has a Deep Sea Blue Metallic exterior and an Black interior color. 41,522 miles. Stock Number 25654A. You can connect with us by calling (864) 580-2400. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: DEEP SEA BLUE METALLIC Driving Assistance Package ($950 value)
  • Rear View Camera
  • Park Distance Control
XLine ($1,500 value)
  • 19\' X 8.5\' Light Alloy Y-Spoke (style 608) Wheels
  • Dark Copper High-Gloss Trim
  • XLine
Lighting Package ($900 value)
  • Xenon Headlights
  • Adaptive Light Control
Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Ready to drive home this 2017 BMW X3 sDrive28i today at Spartanburg Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram or Call us at (864) 580-2400 to schedule your visit. Don't miss out - at this price $$16,700 it won't last long! Visit Spartanburg Dodge Chrysler Jeep at 8200 Fairforest Rd, Spartanburg, SC 29303 today!

(2) Keys/remotes.Purchasing a locally owned, non-smoker, clean CARFAX Used 2017 Mercedes-Benz GLE AMG GLE 43 offers the ideal combination of a well-maintained vehicle and the inherent performance, luxury, and value of the AMG GLE 43. * Assured Health & Hygiene: A certified non-smoker vehicle ensures a fresh interior free from the persistent and harmful "thirdhand smoke" residue and odors that are nearly impossible to remove completely from upholstery and air vents. This also protects the health of future passengers. * Peace of Mind with a Clean CARFAX: A clean CARFAX report, indicating no major accidents, flood damage, or salvage titles, provides crucial transparency into the car's past and helps you avoid potential "lemons" with undisclosed issues. * Higher Resale Value: The combination of a clean history, non-smoking interior, and detailed records means the vehicle will likely retain a higher resale value when you decide to sell or trade it in. * Powerful Engine: The 2017 Mercedes-AMG GLE 43 features a potent 3.0-liter twin-turbocharged V6 engine, producing 362 horsepower and 384 lb-ft of torque, offering a thrilling and adventurous driving experience. * Luxurious Comfort: Reviewers consistently praise the GLE 43 for its exceptional comfort and well-built, upscale interior, featuring high-quality materials, available massaging seats, and ample passenger room.

Check out this 2017 BMW X6 M available at Parks Chevrolet of Spartanburg, SC. Offered at just $29,991, this BMW X6 M won't last long. This all-wheel drive BMW X6 M is powered by a 4.4L V8 DOHC 32V TwinPower Turbo engine with only 81,605 miles and includes these features and benefits.

• Leather

This BMW X6 M offers a thrilling driving experience with its powerful turbocharged V8 engine and sport-tuned all-wheel drive system. The luxurious interior features premium leather upholstery, a state-of-the-art navigation system, and a premium harman/kardon surround sound system to keep you entertained on every drive. The hands-free power liftgate and memory seats provide added convenience, while the advanced safety technologies like the backup camera and rain-sensing wipers give you peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're looking for a capable and dynamic SUV or a high-performance luxury vehicle, this 2017 BMW X6 M delivers an uncompromising blend of power, style, and sophistication. With its sleek Donington Gray Metallic exterior, this BMW X6 M is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Don't miss your chance to experience the thrill of driving this exceptional BMW X6 M. Schedule a test drive today and discover why it's the ultimate choice for the discerning driver. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional performance, premium features, and unparalleled driving dynamics.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, power, and luxury in this exceptional 2017 Cadillac XT5 Premium Luxury. With its sleek exterior, refined interior, and impressive performance, this versatile crossover is the ultimate expression of Cadillac's commitment to excellence.

Highlighted features include:
• Navigation System
• Bose Studio Surround Sound with 14 Speakers
• Adaptive Suspension
• Panoramic Sunroof
• Power Liftgate
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Automatic Dual-Zone Climate Control

The XT5's stunning Dark Granite Metallic exterior exudes confidence and sophistication, while the spacious and well-appointed cabin offers a sanctuary of comfort and convenience. Settle into the premium leather seats and experience the seamless integration of the Cadillac CUE infotainment system, providing intuitive control over your music, navigation, and more.

Under the hood, the potent 3.6L V6 engine delivers a thrilling driving experience, effortlessly blending power and efficiency. With 19 city/27 highway MPG, you can enjoy the open road without compromise.

Elevate your driving experience with the XT5's advanced safety features, including Forward Collision Alert, Lane Departure Warning, and Rear Park Assist. These cutting-edge technologies work tirelessly to help keep you and your loved ones secure.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure or seeking a luxurious daily commuter, this 2017 Cadillac XT5 Premium Luxury is the perfect companion. Experience the difference that Cadillac craftsmanship and attention to detail can make. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this exceptional vehicle deserves a place in your driveway.

Discover the ultimate in luxury and capability with this stunning 2017 Ford Explorer Platinum. This top-of-the-line SUV is the perfect blend of power, technology, and refined style, making it the ideal choice for the discerning driver.

• Front & Rear Floor Liners

Slip behind the wheel and experience the unparalleled comfort of the Nirvana Multi Contour Leather Cooled Bucket Seats, which offer exceptional support and ventilation. The premium audio system from Sony will immerse you in your favorite music, while the SYNC 3 infotainment system provides seamless connectivity and intuitive controls.

The 3.5L V6 engine delivers robust performance, effortlessly handling any terrain with the confidence of 4-Wheel Drive. Enjoy the convenience of the Power Liftgate and the added safety of features like the Lane Departure Warning System and Auto High-Beam Headlights.

This Explorer Platinum is more than just a vehicle – it's a statement of refined taste and uncompromising quality. With its stunning Gray exterior and an impressive list of premium amenities, this SUV is poised to exceed your expectations.

Imagine the thrill of commanding the road in this exceptional Ford Explorer Platinum. Its powerful engine, advanced technology, and luxurious appointments come together to create a driving experience that is truly unparalleled. Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a weekend adventure, this SUV will elevate every journey.

At our dealership, we take pride in offering our customers the finest vehicles on the market. This 2017 Ford Explorer Platinum is a testament to our commitment to excellence, and we are confident that it will exceed your expectations. We invite you to schedule a test drive and experience the unmatched performance, comfort, and style of this remarkable SUV for yourself.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional Ford Explorer Platinum. Contact us today to learn more and take the first step towards driving home in the vehicle of your dreams.

The 2017 Honda CR-V Touring is a top-of-the-line compact SUV that combines premium comfort, advanced technology, and Honda’s legendary reliability, now available at Sam Boswell Honda. Known for excellent fuel efficiency, strong resale value, and a spacious interior, the 2017 CR-V Touring is a perfect choice for families, commuters, and anyone searching for a dependable and luxurious compact SUV 🚙✨

Under the hood, the 2017 Honda CR-V Touring delivers responsive performance with smooth acceleration and confident handling for both city driving and highway travel. All-wheel drive capability enhances traction and control in changing road conditions, while Honda Sensing safety features such as adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, collision mitigation braking, and road departure mitigation provide added peace of mind. With flexible seating, generous cargo space, and a quiet ride, this CR-V Touring is built to handle daily life and weekend getaways with ease 🛣️💪

Inside, the 2017 Honda CR-V Touring offers a premium interior loaded with upscale features including leather-trimmed seating, heated front seats, power-adjustable driver’s seat, navigation, and a large touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and Bluetooth connectivity. Spacious passenger room, a power tailgate, and thoughtful storage solutions make every drive more comfortable and convenient.   • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Predictive brake assist - Be prepared for your big brake. Predictive brake assist monitors the available distance in front of you compared to your vehicles speed. If your speed exceeds the required distance to stop short of a collision, it readies your brakes to apply maximum stopping force when you use them. Predictive brake assist helps see to it that you stop.

description: Embark on a luxurious journey in this sleek Silver 2017 Lexus RX 350! Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 engine paired with an efficient 8-speed automatic transmission, this front-wheel drive beauty offers a smooth and responsive driving experience. With its striking chrome accents and sporty lip spoiler, this Lexus commands attention on the road. Sink into the plush leather seats and enjoy the premium sound system with 9 speakers as you cruise in comfort. The spacious interior is filled with upscale amenities like dual-zone air conditioning, a power moonroof, and a convenient power liftgate. Safety is paramount with features like a pre-collision system, front and rear airbags, and a tire pressure monitoring system. Plus, rest assured knowing that a Carfax report is available for your peace of mind. Packed with convenience features such as a HomeLink garage door transmitter and a cargo area roll-up cover, this Lexus RX 350 is the epitome of style and sophistication. Don't miss your chance to own this luxurious ride - it's the perfect blend of elegance and performance! Visit United Auto Group online at uagdallas.com to see more pictures of this vehicle or call us at 469-766-1034 today to schedule your test drive.

AutoNation Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram North Fort Worth is excited to offer this 2017 Chevrolet Tahoe LT. This Chevrolet Tahoe offers all the comforts of a well-optioned sedan with the utility you demand from an SUV. Is it possible to fall in love with a vehicle? It is when your vehicle is as prestige as the Chevrolet Tahoe. Look no further, you have found exactly what you've been looking for. More information about the 2017 Chevrolet Tahoe: The Suburban and Tahoe are by far the best-selling models in their class, and they're tough rivals for the Ford Expedition, Toyota Sequoia and Nissan Armada, among others. These two Chevy models are closely related in most ways--although there's a key difference: the Suburban is 14 inches longer in wheelbase and 20 inches longer overall than the Tahoe, and that results in a significantly larger third-row seat than in the Tahoe--as well as easier access to it, and more cargo space. Compared to rival models, the Chevy Tahoe and Suburban stand out for their ride quality and relatively efficient engines. They're also very rugged and versatile, and can be outfitted for off-road toughness, tow ability and interior luxury as needed. Chevrolet claims that the Suburban will be the most fuel-efficient model in the full-size SUV class, thanks to tech such as direct injection and active fuel management (cylinder deactivation). Although the profile of the Suburban and Tahoe haven't changed all that much, Chevy has managed to make significant improvements to aerodynamics. Chiseled sheet metal and big, flamboyant wheels (up to 22 inches) help maintain a powerful look. This model sets itself apart with Much-improved interior, seating space, towing ability, versatility and toughness, comfortable, refined ride, and relatively fuel-efficient engines

description:
CarFax No Accidents! Popular Options and Features Include: Convenience
  • Cruise control maintains a preset vehicle speed, automatically increasing or decreasing throttle to maintain that speed.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • In normal driving conditions, automatic full-time 4-wheel drive directs power to one axle, or 2-wheel drive. When the primary axle senses wheel spin or slippage, some or all available torque is automatically transferred to the secondary axle. No driver input is required. The system may or may not have 4WD-Low capabilities.
  • All-wheel drive supplies power to both the front and rear axles all the time. Power is instantly redirected by the center differential to the wheels with greater traction when slip is detected. Unlike full-time 4-wheel drive systems, there is no 2-speed transfer case for 4WD Low operation.
  • Variable valve control allows the lift, duration and/or timing of the intake or exhaust valves to be altered while the engine is in operation.
  • The engine configuration is four cylinders arranged in a straight line.
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • Brake assist senses panic braking from the speed of the brake pedal's travel and applies all available power brake boost.

description:
Experience the pinnacle of SUV luxury and capability with this 2017 GMC Yukon XL SLT. Boasting a powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and a sleek beige exterior, this Yukon XL is ready to take on any adventure with ease.

Standout features include:
• Open Road Package with additional SiriusXM and navigation
• 20" polished aluminum wheels
• Power release second-row bucket seats
• HD Trailering Package with integrated trailer brake controller
• Premium Smooth Ride Suspension Package
• Hands-free power liftgate
• Wireless charging
• Rear-seat Blu-Ray/DVD entertainment system

The Yukon XL's impressive size and capability make it the perfect choice for families, outdoor enthusiasts, and those who need to tow heavy loads. With seating for up to eight and a cavernous cargo area, this SUV offers unparalleled versatility and space.

Beyond its impressive utility, the Yukon XL SLT is a true luxury vehicle. Indulge in the comfort of heated and ventilated leather-appointed seats, a heated steering wheel, and a power tilt-and-telescoping steering column. Stay connected with the cutting-edge IntelliLink infotainment system, complete with navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert to help you navigate the road with confidence. The Yukon XL's robust construction and advanced safety systems provide a reassuring sense of security for you and your loved ones.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip, towing a boat or trailer, or simply seeking a premium SUV for your daily drives, this 2017 GMC Yukon XL SLT is the perfect choice. Experience the perfect blend of power, technology, and refinement. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional SUV for a test drive and discover why the Yukon XL is the ultimate choice for discerning drivers.

description: Get ready to embrace the spirit of adventure in this bold Firecracker Red Clearcoat 2017 Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV. Its the quintessential vehicle for those who want to stand out while exploring everything from paved city streets to rugged off-road trails. With its powerful 3.6L V6 engine and heavy-duty suspension with gas shocks, this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV is built to handle tough terrain with absolute confidence. Since it features the iconic 4WD system, you'll never have to worry about where the pavement ends and the adventure begins.This Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV is equipped with the Quick Order Package 24G, which adds body-color appliques to the front and rear bumpers and a matching body-color grille for a sleek, uniform look. You'll love the Black 3-piece hard top that provides a quiet and secure cabin while being easy to remove when you want to feel the wind. The Connectivity Group ensures you stay in touch with the world through Uconnect voice commands and Bluetooth integration. Whether you're using the remote start system to warm up the car or checking the tire pressure display, this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV is packed with practical tech for your daily life.Comfort meets durability inside this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV, featuring heated front seats and a premium leather steering wheel. The interior is designed to be tough yet refined, with genuine wood accents on the console and dashboard adding an unexpected touch of class. You can easily manage your favorite tunes with the steering wheel mounted audio controls while the 8-speaker sound system fills the cabin with high-quality audio. With the Freedom Panel storage bag included, taking the top off your Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV and enjoying the sun is simpler than ever.Safety and visibility are major highlights of this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV, which includes fully automatic headlights and front fog lights to guide your way. The integrated roll-over protection and electronic stability control work together to keep you safe during your travels. You'll also appreciate the heated door mirrors and auto-dimming rearview mirror, which help keep your sightlines clear in various driving conditions. Every part of this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV is engineered to give you peace of mind while you're out making memories.This 2017 Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV comes with a clean CARFAX, showing its been well cared for and is ready for its next owner. It combines the legendary Jeep heritage with modern conveniences like remote keyless entry and a security system. From the anti-spin differential rear axle to the deep-tinted glass, this vehicle is the perfect mix of function and flair. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of the Jeep legacy with this striking and capable Wrangler Unlimited Sahara SUV.Check Availability Now or Call 727-306-9453.727-306-9453 Our Mercedes-Benz Factory Certification program is a curation of the very best Pre-Owned Mercedes-Benz vehicles available. Each and every one has passed a rigorous, 162-point Factory inspection and been completely reconditioned inside and out. All services and maintenance are up to date, including tires, brakes, belts, hoses and all fluids. Comes with 24/7 Roadside Assistance, Trip-Interruption Coverage, CARFAX service records available.

Recently Arrived | Original MSRP $58,600 | AWD | Located at Our Volvo Store

Discover refined Scandinavian design, advanced safety, and confident all-wheel-drive performance in this 2017 Volvo XC90 T6 Momentum AWD, finished in striking Onyx Black Metallic with a charcoal leather interior. This well-equipped luxury SUV has just arrived at Autobahn Volvo in Fort Worth, TX, and with 113,817 miles on the odometer, it represents an outstanding value in a premium three-row SUV.

Power comes from Volvo's responsive T6 I4 supercharged engine paired with an automatic transmission with Geartronic, delivering smooth acceleration and confident passing power. The AWD system enhances traction and stability in changing road conditions, while Volvo's renowned engineering ensures a composed, comfortable ride for daily driving or longer journeys.

Step inside and you're welcomed by a thoughtfully designed cabin that balances luxury and practicality. The charcoal leather seating offers both comfort and durability, and convenience features like a 12V power outlet in the cargo area, grocery bag holder, and HomeLink garage door integration make everyday life easier. The included Protection Package Plus* adds an extra layer of care for your vehicle, helping preserve its premium look and feel.

This XC90 is loaded with advanced technology and driver-assistance features that Volvo is famous for. Highlights include the 360-Degree Surround View Camera for confident parking and maneuvering, BLIS Blind Spot Information System, Lane Keeping Aid, and Park Assist Pilot. The Pilot Assist Driver Assistance System adds support during highway driving, helping reduce fatigue on longer trips. Additional features like automatically dimming exterior mirrors, power retractable exterior mirrors, digital compass, and the Vision Package further enhance visibility and peace of mind.

At Autobahn Volvo, we use market-based pricing, so you can be confident this XC90 is priced very well within current market conditions. We offer a wide variety of vehicles, including several pre-owned Volvo and Audi models, making it easy to find an excellent vehicle at a price you can feel good about. We also provide nationwide delivery, and for added confidence, extended service contracts are available on this vehicle for peace of mind.

This 2017 Volvo XC90 T6 Momentum AWD is located at our Volvo store and is available now. To experience it up close without leaving home, ask your sales associate for a virtual walkaround and see every detail from the comfort of your own space.

*Call (817)-390-3236 today to learn more or to schedule your virtual walkaround. Don't miss the opportunity to own this well-equipped, safety-focused luxury SUV-Recent Arrival and ready for its next adventure.

description: Embrace the perfect combination of rugged capability and refined luxury with this 2017 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited. Finished in a clean Bright White Clearcoat, this 4WD SUV is powered by a reliable 3.6L V6 engine, making it just as comfortable navigating city streets as it is exploring a dirt trail. With Jeep's legendary four-wheel-drive system and specialized Off-Road Display Pages in the instrument cluster, you'll have all the information you need to tackle your next adventure with confidence.Inside, the cabin is designed to be your sanctuary. You'll find Leather-Trimmed Bucket Seats that are not only stylish but incredibly functional offering Heated Front and Rear Seats to keep everyone cozy during chilly mornings. The driver also benefits from a Heated Steering Wheel and a memory system that saves your preferred seat and mirror positions. Whether you're heading out on a long trip or just running to the store, the Power Sunroof adds an airy, open feel to every drive.Staying connected is a breeze with the Uconnect 3C Navigation system. The large 8.4" Touchscreen Display features GPS Navigation, HD Radio, and Integrated Voice Command with Bluetooth, allowing you to control your media and maps without distraction. For added convenience, this Grand Cherokee includes a Power Liftgate for easy cargo loading and a garage door transmitter to make arriving home seamless.Safety is built into every mile of this Jeep. It comes equipped with Blind Spot and Cross Path Detection to alert you of vehicles you might not see, while the ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera makes reversing into tight spots simple. Features like auto-dimming mirrors and speed-sensitive wipers work behind the scenes to ensure your visibility is always clear, no matter the time of day or the weather outside.At the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville, we pride ourselves on making the car-buying process straightforward and enjoyable. This Grand Cherokee has been professionally cleaned and serviced, ensuring it meets our high standards so you can drive away feeling like you've bought a brand-new vehicle. Come by today to see how easy it is to find your next favorite ride!Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.

This 2017 Hyundai Tucson SE Ruby Wine with a Beige interior. This Hyundai Tucson comes with the following features: Convenience
  • Cruise control maintains a preset vehicle speed, automatically increasing or decreasing throttle to maintain that speed.
  • A handheld keyfob capable of remotely operating all the door locks.
In-car Entertainment
  • The vehicle can directly access and control digital memory stored on a hard-drive or memory card/stick. Digital memory can contain audio, video, pictures, or general files.
Safety and Security
  • Brake assist senses panic braking from the speed of the brake pedal's travel and applies all available power brake boost.
  • When starting from an incline position, the vehicle automatically applies brake force to prevent itself from rolling back.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
Technology and Telematics
  • Otherwise known as Bluetooth, this technology allows electronic devices to integrate with the vehicle systems without the need for a physical connection between them.

If you’re looking for a local car dealership that offers new INFINITIs, used vehicles of all makes and models, exceptional service, and multiple finance options we’ve got you covered. Looking for used vehicles for sale in Oklahoma City? At Bob Moore INFINITI we have a large assortment of used vehicles including a variety of makes and models. While we carry many used makes and models, we also carry used INFINITIs in case you aren’t looking for new models. If you’re still trying to decide which model and trim is the best fit, we can get you with one of our certified INFINITI specialists to go over all the details — whether it’s regarding features, warranties, service, financing, or any other areas you’d like addressed. Our dealership also offers a variety of amenities, free Wi-Fi, and all kinds of perks. For those wishing to shop for their car online, we can help you with that as well. When buying an used vehicle, we want to make sure you get your money’s worth. To ensure this, we put all our used vehicles through a service reconditioning process. We make sure the tires have three 30-second tire depths or 30%, if they don’t, we’ll replace the tires. We’ll also replace any brakes over 3mm. After the vehicles full inspection, it leaves the shop and goes through cosmetic refurbishing where we inspect and replace scratches, dents, scuffs, and road rash, as well as interior leather and upholstery reconditioning. While we work hard to ensure the quality of all used vehicles, we must acknowledge that some will end up with defects. Speak with one of our sales specialists about an used vehicle you’re interested in to get a history of the car.
