description: Are you ready to embrace the spirit of adventure and freedom? Introducing the 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon, a remarkable blend of rugged capability and refined comfort. With its iconic design and legendary 4x4 prowess, this SUV is built to conquer both the urban jungle and the unbeaten path. Let’s dive into what makes this vehicle an irresistible choice for thrill-seekers and daily drivers alike! First impressions matter, and the pristine white exterior of this Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon is sure to turn heads wherever you go. Its bold, timeless design is complemented by robust off-road features, including the signature seven-slot grille and round headlamps. The sturdy build and elevated stance not only enhance its commanding presence but also signal readiness for any terrain. Step inside, and you’ll be greeted by a world of comfort and style. The interior boasts luxurious black leather seats, providing an inviting contrast to the rugged exterior. This harmonious blend of toughness and elegance ensures that every journey, whether it’s a cross-country road trip or a quick city commute, is enjoyed in supreme comfort. The spacious cabin offers ample room for passengers and cargo, making it perfect for family adventures or solo escapades. Under the hood lies the heart of this beast – a robust 3.6L V6 engine that delivers an impressive 285 horsepower and 260 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a smooth 5-speed automatic transmission, this powerhouse is engineered to provide an exhilarating driving experience. Whether you’re navigating rocky trails or cruising down the highway, the Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon offers unmatched performance and reliability. One of the standout features of this Rubicon is its award-winning reputation. It proudly holds the title of Kelley Blue Book's 5-Year Cost to Own: Best Mid-Size SUV/Crossover, ensuring that your investment is not only thrilling but also financially sound. Additionally, it’s recognized for its exceptional resale value, having been awarded Kelley Blue Book's Best Resale Value: Mid-Size SUV/Crossover. These accolades speak volumes about the vehicle’s enduring quality and desirability. The 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon comes equipped with a suite of manufacturer options and packages designed to enhance your driving experience. While specifics aren’t listed here, rest assured that Jeep’s commitment to quality and innovation means you’ll enjoy a host of features that cater to both convenience and adventure. With 119,771 miles on the odometer, this Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon has proven its reliability and durability. It’s a testament to Jeep’s engineering prowess, ready to offer countless more miles of exploration and excitement. In conclusion, the 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon is more than just a vehicle, it’s a lifestyle statement. It’s for those who crave adventure without sacrificing comfort, and for those who value a vehicle with a proven track record of quality and performance. Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional SUV. Embrace the adventure, seize the moment, and make this iconic Jeep yours today!

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

This 2017 Subaru Forester Limited, has a Dark Gray Metallic exterior and Gray interior color with only 95,425 miles. Stock Number 66506A. You can connect with us by calling 781-246-3331. No Accidents! One Owner! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Base Model
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Discover the perfect blend of capability and sophistication in this 2017 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited 4WD. With its rugged 4WD performance, refined interior, and impressive technology features, this Grand Cherokee is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• **LOCAL TRADE IN**
• RADIO: UCONNECT 3C W/8.4" DISPLAY
• Roadside Assistance & 9-1-1 Call
• Instrument Cluster w/Off-Road Disp, Pages
• Uconnect Access
• 8.4" Touchscreen Display
• Integrated Voice Command w/Bluetooth
• Nav-Capable! See Dealer for Details
• Quick Order Package 23H

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Grand Cherokee delivers an impressive 18 city/25 highway MPG, making it both capable and efficient. Beneath the sleek gray exterior lies a refined interior that pampers you with features like heated front and rear seats, a heated steering wheel, and a premium audio system.

The Uconnect 3C system with an 8.4" display puts a wealth of connectivity and information at your fingertips. Enjoy seamless integration with your smartphone, turn-by-turn navigation, and intuitive voice commands. The available off-road pages in the instrument cluster provide valuable data to enhance your adventures.

Safety is also a top priority, with advanced features like Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Path Detection, and a ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera to help you navigate with confidence. The Jeep Grand Cherokee's legendary 4WD capability, combined with its premium amenities and technology, make it the ideal choice for those seeking a versatile and refined SUV.

Experience the exceptional capabilities and refined luxury of this 2017 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited 4WD. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover how this exceptional vehicle can elevate your driving experience.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2017 Lexus NX 200t AWD. This meticulously maintained luxury crossover boasts a sleek black exterior and a wealth of premium features that will captivate the discerning buyer.

Standout attributes of this vehicle include:

• Accident-free history and a single previous owner
• Navigation System Package and Premium Package for enhanced convenience and luxury
• Impressive list of premium features, including:
- Heated and ventilated front seats
- Panoramic moonroof
- Lexus Enform connectivity suite
- Alloy wheels and high-clearance lamps
- Power tilt and slide moonroof
- Heated door mirrors and electronic stability control

The 2.0L 16-valve DOHC engine, paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission and Lexus' renowned AWD system, delivers a dynamic and confident driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 22 mpg in the city, this NX 200t offers a compelling balance of performance and efficiency.

Slip behind the wheel and you'll be surrounded by a wealth of thoughtful amenities, from dual-zone climate control and a premium audio system to the convenience of a power driver's seat with memory settings. The spacious cabin and generous cargo capacity make this Lexus an ideal companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

This 2017 Lexus NX 200t AWD represents an exceptional value in the luxury crossover segment. With its impeccable history, premium features, and Lexus' renowned reputation for quality and reliability, it's a vehicle that will captivate the discerning buyer. We invite you to experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of Lexus ownership.

Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and capability with this 2017 Toyota RAV4 Hybrid XLE. This exceptional SUV offers the best of both worlds - the spaciousness and versatility you need, combined with the impressive fuel economy you desire.

• Front dual zone A/C
• Remote keyless entry
• Traction control
• ABS brakes
• Low tire pressure warning
• Power moonroof
• Electronic Stability Control
• Active Cruise Control
• Heated door mirrors
• Illuminated entry
• Alloy wheels

Powered by a 2.5L 4-cylinder engine and CVT transmission with AWD, this RAV4 Hybrid delivers an outstanding 34 MPG in the city and 30 MPG on the highway. The advanced hybrid system provides a seamless blend of electric and gasoline power, ensuring a smooth, responsive, and efficient driving experience.

Beyond its exceptional efficiency, this RAV4 Hybrid is packed with a wealth of premium features that elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures. Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone climate control, the versatility of a power liftgate, and the confidence of advanced safety technologies like Blind Spot Monitoring and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert.

The spacious and well-appointed interior offers ample room for passengers and cargo, with split-folding rear seats and a generous cargo area. Settle into the comfortable and supportive front seats, which feature premium fabric upholstery and power adjustability.

Connectivity is seamless thanks to the Entune Audio Plus system, featuring a 7-inch touchscreen, SiriusXM satellite radio, and Bluetooth integration for hands-free calls and audio streaming.

Whether you're seeking a capable and efficient family SUV or a versatile companion for your active lifestyle, this 2017 Toyota RAV4 Hybrid XLE is an exceptional choice. Experience the perfect balance of performance, technology, and comfort. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable vehicle for a test drive and discover how it can enhance your driving experience.

description: 4WD!!! HARD TO FIND!!! ONLY 73,500 MILES!!! LOADED!!! NAVIGATION!!! LEATHER SEATS!!! HEATED AND POWER SEATS!!! POWER THIRD ROW SEATING!!! AND MORE!!! PLEASE HURRY!!! PRICED TO SELL!!!.Unlike other models dubbed "Sport," the 2017 Explorer Sport is indeed sporty, thanks to its turbocharged 3.5-liter V6 with 290HP, stiffer suspension tuning, quicker steering and our test vehicle's optional summer performance tires. The result is lots of speed and impressive handling and braking.The Explorer drives bigger than it is. Its well-damped ride prioritizes comfort over dynamic handling a blessing on rough roads or long road trips, but a curse for those who enjoy taking a winding route home. The Explorer's ride-and-handling balance toes the line expected of players in this class, and its body control in corners is par for the segment.While the materials used in our top-of-the-line Platinum test vehicle were of high quality, cabin fit and finish were horrid panels fit together poorly, and gaps were large. Spacious accommodations, comfortable front seats, and solid ergonomics are the interiors few saving graces. As in the front row, second-row passengers are treated to impressive amounts of legroom and headroom.

The 2017 Subaru Forester 2.5i Premium comes equipped with the following upgrades and options:

- All-Weather Package (Heated Front Seats, Heated Exterior Mirrors, Windshield Wiper De-Icer)
- Crystal Black Silica Door Edge Guards
- Rear Bumper Cover

This Forester is the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and style. With Subaru's legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, you'll have confidence and control in any driving condition. The 2.5-liter 4-cylinder BOXER engine delivers an impressive 26 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, making it both powerful and efficient.

Inside, the premium cloth upholstery and heated front seats provide a luxurious and comfortable ride, while the 7-inch Starlink multimedia system with SiriusXM keeps you connected and entertained. The power driver's seat, tilt/telescoping steering wheel, and steering wheel-mounted controls make it easy to find your perfect driving position.

Versatility is key with the Forester's 60/40 split-folding rear seats and generous cargo space. Whether you're hauling gear for your next adventure or running errands around town, this Subaru has the space and flexibility to handle it all.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Subaru's advanced airbag system, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera to help you navigate with confidence.

Experience the Forester's exceptional combination of capability, comfort, and technology for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover why the Subaru Forester is the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

description:
Introducing the rugged and powerful 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport, equipped with a 3.6L V6 engine that boasts an impressive 285 horsepower and 260 foot-pounds of torque. This versatile vehicle is ready for any adventure, whether it's hitting the trails or cruising through the city.

Featuring a spacious interior with comfortable seating for up to five passengers, the Wrangler Unlimited Sport offers ample room for you and your loved ones. The iconic Jeep design, with its signature seven-slot grille and round headlights, gives this vehicle a classic and timeless look that will turn heads wherever you go.

But don't let its stylish appearance fool you, the Wrangler Unlimited Sport is built for tough terrain. With its renowned 4x4 capability and high ground clearance, this Jeep can conquer any obstacle in its path. Plus, the Unlimited Sport comes with a range of available off-road features, such as a heavy-duty suspension and all-terrain tires, to enhance its off-roading capabilities.

On top of its impressive performance and off-roading capabilities, the Wrangler Unlimited Sport also offers a range of modern features for your convenience and entertainment. The Uconnect infotainment system allows for easy access to music, navigation, and hands-free calling, while the available Alpine premium audio system ensures a top-notch listening experience.

Don't miss out on the chance to own this 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport. With its powerful engine, rugged design, and modern features, it's the perfect vehicle for those who want to take on any adventure. Come in for a test drive and experience the thrill of driving a Jeep today!

description: The 2017 BMW X5 xDrive40e iPerformance is a premium plug-in hybrid SUV that expertly combines luxury, efficiency, and performance. With its distinctive design and advanced features, the X5 xDrive40e offers a comfortable and refined driving experience. The exterior is both sleek and bold, featuring signature BMW styling cues complemented by striking Xenon headlights that enhance visibility and add a sophisticated touch. The expansive panoramic sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating an open and airy atmosphere for all passengers, while the hands-free liftgate offers added convenience for loading and unloading cargo with ease.----Inside, the X5 xDrive40e blends luxury with technology. Leather seats provide plush comfort and a premium feel, making long drives more enjoyable. The intuitive navigation system ensures you're always on the right path, offering guidance with precision and ease. A sunroof feature adds an extra touch of sophistication to this already well-appointed interior. As a plug-in hybrid, the xDrive40e offers both electric-only driving capability and the flexibility of a gasoline engine, delivering an efficient yet powerful performance. With BMW's intelligent all-wheel-drive system (xDrive), the vehicle is ready to handle varying road conditions confidently. The 2017 X5 xDrive40e iPerformance is a well-rounded SUV that meets the needs of those looking for luxury, performance, and eco-conscious driving.

2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier SUV for Sale at SUPERSTAR MOTORZ in Milwaukie, OregonLooking for the ultimate combination of luxury, power, and versatility? The 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier SUV is waiting for you at SUPERSTAR MOTORZ in Milwaukie, Clackamas, Oregon. This full-size SUV is the perfect companion for families, adventurers, and anyone who demands more from their vehicle. With its robust performance, cutting-edge features, and spacious interior, the Suburban Premier is ready to elevate your driving experience.Power and Performance: The Heart of the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban PremierUnder the hood of the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier lies the formidable EcoTec3 5.3L Flex Fuel V8 engine. Delivering an impressive 355 horsepower and 383 lb-ft of torque, this SUV is built to handle whatever your journey demands. Whether you're towing a trailer, navigating rugged terrain, or cruising through city streets, the 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission ensures smooth and responsive performance. The 4WD capability provides added confidence and control, making the Suburban Premier a reliable choice for all seasons and conditions.Luxury Meets Functionality: Inside the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban PremierStep inside the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier, and you'll find a spacious and luxurious interior designed with your comfort in mind. With seating for up to eight passengers, this SUV is perfect for family road trips, carpooling, or weekend getaways. Premium materials, meticulous craftsmanship, and thoughtful design details create an upscale atmosphere that everyone will appreciate.The Suburban Premier is equipped with advanced technology to keep you connected and entertained on the go. Features like a touchscreen infotainment system, smartphone integration, and a premium sound system ensure that every drive is enjoyable. Plus, with ample cargo space and customizable seating configurations, this SUV adapts to your lifestyle with ease.Exterior Design: Bold, Stylish, and CommandingThe 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier makes a statement wherever it goes. Its bold and commanding presence is complemented by sleek lines, a distinctive grille, and eye-catching chrome accents. The attention to detail in the exterior design not only enhances the Suburban's aesthetics but also improves its aerodynamics for better performance and efficiency. Available in a range of sophisticated colors, this SUV is sure to turn heads on the road.Practical features such as roof rails and a power liftgate add convenience to your adventures. Whether you're loading up for a camping trip or picking up groceries, the Suburban Premier is designed to make your life easier and more enjoyable.Safety and Confidence: The 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier DeliversSafety is a top priority in the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier. Packed with advanced safety features, this SUV is built to protect you and your loved ones on every journey. From its robust construction to its suite of driver-assistance technologies, the Suburban Premier offers peace of mind behind the wheel.Features like forward collision alert, lane keep assist, and rear cross-traffic alert help you stay aware of your surroundings and avoid potential hazards. Additionally, the rearview camera and parking sensors make maneuvering in tight spaces a breeze. With the Suburban Premier, you can drive with confidence knowing that your safety is in good hands.Why Choose the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier?The 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier stands out in the full-size SUV segment for its exceptional blend of power, luxury, and practicality. Whether you're tackling tough terrain, transporting a large group, or simply enjoying a comfortable commute, this SUV delivers on all fronts. Its reputation for reliability and performance makes it a smart investment for anyone in need of a versatile and capable vehicle.At SUPERSTAR MOTORZ in Milwaukie, Clackamas, Oregon, we take pride in offering high-quality vehicles like the 2017 Chevrolet Suburban Premier. This top trim Santa Fe combines upscale comfort, turbocharged performance, and cutting-edge technology in one beautifully designed SUV. description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and versatility in this stunning 2017 Ford Escape Titanium. With its sleek gold exterior and a wealth of premium features, this SUV is poised to exceed your expectations and elevate your driving experience.

• Equipment Group 300A
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Rear Parking Sensors
• Heated front seats
• Wheels: 18" Sparkle Silver-Painted Aluminum

Slip behind the wheel and you'll be greeted by the SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System, providing seamless connectivity and intuitive control over your music, navigation, and more. The 1.5L EcoBoost engine delivers a thrilling yet efficient performance, with an impressive 30 highway MPG to keep you moving with confidence.

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, this Escape Titanium boasts a wealth of premium amenities. Enjoy the convenience of a power liftgate, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a memory driver's seat that remembers your perfect settings. The heated leather-trimmed seats and steering wheel will keep you cozy on even the chilliest days.

Safety is paramount, and this Escape Titanium delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced features. From the Rear Parking Sensors and Exterior Parking Camera Rear to the Emergency Communication System and Airbag Protection, you can drive with peace of mind knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure or tackling your daily commute, this 2017 Ford Escape Titanium is the perfect companion. With its exceptional versatility, dynamic performance, and refined luxury, it's a vehicle that will elevate your driving experience and leave a lasting impression.

Experience the difference for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this Escape Titanium is the perfect choice for you.

RX 350 trim. EPA 26 MPG Hwy/19 MPG City! Heated Seats, Sunroof, Navigation, Onboard Communications System, iPod/MP3 Input, Satellite Radio, Back-Up Camera, All Wheel Drive, Alloy Wheels, HEATED ESPRESSO WALNUT STEERING WHEEL... AND MORE!

KEY FEATURES INCLUDE
All Wheel Drive, Back-Up Camera, Satellite Radio, iPod/MP3 Input, Onboard Communications System. Lexus RX 350 with Silver Lining Metallic exterior and STRATUS GRAY interior features a V6 Cylinder Engine with 295 HP at 6300 RPM*.

OPTION PACKAGES
12.3 NAVIGATION SYSTEM: advanced voice command casual-language voice recognition system, Bluetooth® hands free phone and automatic phonebook download capabilities, remote touch navigation controller, HD Radio w/iTunes tagging, SiriusXM NavTraffic, NavWeather, Sports, Stocks and Fuel Prices, Lexus Insider and Electro Multi Vision (EMV) display, Lexus Enform Destinations, Destination Assist, Lexus Enform App Suite, destination search, Yelp, iHeartRadio, Facebook Places, Movietickets.com, OpenTable, Pandora, Slacker, stocks, fuel prices and sports, Single-Disc DVD Changer, WHEELS: 20 X 8 SPLIT 5-SPOKE DARK SILVER: machined finish, Tires: P235/55R20 M+S, POWER TILT & SLIDE MOONROOF, BLIND SPOT MONITOR W/REAR CROSS TRAFFIC ALERT: intuitive parking assist, intelligence clearance and back sonar, and lane change assist, PREMIUM PACKAGE: Rear Armrest Storage Compartment, Aluminum Roof Rails, Driver Seat/Steering/Mirror Memory - 3 Settings, drivers seat Easy Exit (auto away/return), HEATED & VENTILATED FRONT SEATS, HEATED ESPRESSO WALNUT STEERING WHEEL, ESPRESSO WALNUT INTERIOR WOOD TRIM, ACCESSORY PACKAGE Key Gloves, Alloy Wheel Locks, Carpet Cargo Mat, Cargo Net, TOUCH-FREE POWER REAR DOOR.

EXPERTS CONCLUDE
KBB.com explains The RXs V6 is both powerful and impressively smooth, matched to an 8-speed automatic that should be the standard by which all automatics are judged..

SERVICE COMPLETED
Service Work completed on this Lexus RX 350 included: Complete Multi-Point Inspection, Oil & Filter Change by a Factory Trained Technician, Battery Voltage Test, Tires Inspected, Brake Inspection, Emissions System Check, Professional Detailed Inside and Out, Function Test all Lights, Check the Complete Exhaust System, Cooling System Inspection, Transmission Fluid Inspection, Differential Fluid Inspection, Function Test all Options & Accessories.

WHO WE ARE
We here at Lexus of Lexington have made it our mission to provide a first class car-shopping experience to our valued customers throughout Lexington, Frankfort KY, Georgetown KY and Richmond KY. With our vast selection of new and used cars, youll have the chance to browse our current inventory in a comfortable, stress-free shopping environment. Visit us to take a test drive, learn more about financing or service your car and we can assure that youll always be well taken care of!

Vehicle Details
2017 Lexus RX 350 Base — 4WD, V6 3.5L Gasoline — Louisville KY. Exceptional value: best price on this luxury crossover. This Lexus RX 350 combines refined performance, reliability, and comfort for drivers who want a premium ride without premium cost. Performance and drivetrain: smooth 3.5L V6 engine paired with dependable 4WD for confident handling in rain or snow. The Lexus RX 350 delivers composed acceleration, quiet cabin, and efficient highway cruising. Comfort and convenience: premium leather seats provide long-trip comfort, rear parking sensors make tight downtown parking simple, hands-free Bluetooth keeps calls and media connected safely while driving. Advanced safety features include blind spot monitor and lane keep assist to help prevent accidents and enhance driver confidence. Interior and tech: spacious cabin with supportive seating, intuitive controls, and quality materials throughout. Ideal for families or professionals who value comfort and safety. Located in Louisville, KY, this pre-owned 2017 Lexus RX 350 Base is competitively priced to sell quickly. Don't miss the best price on a well-maintained luxury crossover with key safety and convenience features. Schedule a test drive in Louisville today to experience the refined ride, practical tech, and confident handling of this Lexus RX 350. Financing options available.

Equipment
This 2017 Lexus RX 350 has a clean CARFAX vehicle history report. Lane Keep Assist in this mid-size suv helps maintain safe driving by gently steering to stay within the lane. The state of the art park assist system will guide you easily into any spot. This unit enhances safety with a blind spot monitor, alerting drivers to potential dangers in adjacent lanes. Bluetooth technology is built into the vehicle, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. Keep your hands warm all winter with a heated steering wheel in this mid-size suv . This vehicle keeps you comfortable with Auto Climate. The leather seats in this vehicle are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. Protect this unit from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this mid-size suv is easy with the climate control system.

Packages
Premium Package Includes: Leather Trim Seats. Power-folding Outside Mirrors. Driver's Seat/Steering Wheel/Mirror Memory. Aluminum Roof Rails: Aluminum Roof Rails, Driver Seat/steering/mirror Memory - 3 Settings, Leather Seat Trim, Rear Armrest Storage Compartment. Cargo Net. Cargo Mat. Wheel Locks & Key Glove: Alloy Wheel Locks, Cargo Net, Key Gloves, Carpet Cargo Mat. Power Tilt and Slide Moonroof. Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Cross Traffic Alert. Heated and Ventilated Front Seats. Matte Linear Dark Mocha Wood Interior Trim. 3500 lbs Tow Prep Package. All-Weather Floor Liners and Cargo Tray. Touch-Free Power Rear Door. Heated Leather Steering Wheel. Carpet Cargo Mat. Alloy Wheel Locks. Cargo Net. Key Gloves. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

description:
Discover the ultimate in off-road adventure and on-road style with this exceptional 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport. Boasting a rugged 3.6L V6 engine, 4-wheel drive capabilities, and a host of premium features, this Wrangler is primed to tackle any terrain while delivering a refined and comfortable driving experience.

Highlights of this Wrangler Unlimited Sport include:
• Dual Top Group with a premium black Sunrider soft top and a durable 3-piece black hard top
• Connectivity Group with Uconnect voice command, Bluetooth, and a tire pressure monitoring display
• Power Convenience Group with remote keyless entry, power locks, and one-touch down front windows
• 17-inch aluminum wheels, power-heated mirrors, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel

This Wrangler's impressive capabilities are matched by its refined interior, which offers comfortable cloth seating, a vehicle information center, and a premium audio system with SiriusXM satellite radio. The deep-tint sunscreen windows and auto-dimming rearview mirror add both style and convenience.

Whether you're seeking the ultimate off-road adventure or a capable and stylish daily driver, this 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport is the perfect choice. With its exceptional features, versatile design, and proven Jeep heritage, this Wrangler is poised to exceed your expectations and deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

Imagine yourself behind the wheel, tackling rugged terrain with confidence and comfort. The Wrangler's legendary 4-wheel-drive system and high-clearance suspension will conquer any challenge, while the premium amenities ensure a refined and enjoyable ride.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2017 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable vehicle for a test drive and discover the true power of Jeep ownership.

Summary
This 2017 Honda CR-V at Oxmoor Ford comes backed by our 3-month, 3,000-mile powertrain warranty—giving you added confidence and peace of mind from the moment you drive off the lot!

Vehicle Details
2017 Honda CR-V EX-L — 4-Cyl 1.5L Gasoline, located in Louisville, KY. This well-maintained compact SUV combines Honda reliability with premium EX-L features at the best price in the area. Powered by a fuel-efficient 1.5L turbocharged 4-cylinder engine and paired with a smooth automatic transmission, this Honda CR-V delivers confident acceleration, excellent highway fuel economy, and a comfortable ride for daily commuting or weekend escapes. The EX-L trim elevates comfort with genuine leather seats and thoughtful conveniences. Automatic climate control ensures a consistently pleasant cabin temperature while adaptive cruise control adds safety and ease on longer drives. Remote start provides quick, weather-ready comfort before you step inside. Seamless smartphone integration with Android Auto keeps navigation, music, and hands-free calling at your fingertips for safer, connected driving. Well-equipped and practical, this Honda CR-V offers generous cargo space, versatile rear seating, and a refined interior layout that prioritizes driver and passenger comfort. Routine maintenance has been performed and the vehicle presents cleanly, reflecting careful ownership. Located in Louisville, KY, this 2017 Honda CR-V EX-L represents exceptional value with a competitive price you won't find elsewhere locally. Schedule a test drive today to experience the combination of performance, comfort, and tech features that make this Honda CR-V an outstanding choice for families and commuters alike.

Equipment
This 2017 Honda CR-V keeps you comfortable with Auto Climate. See what's behind you with the back up camera on this vehicle. This vehicle offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. This Honda CR-V has automated speed control that adjusts to maintain a safe following distance, enhancing highway driving convenience. Start this 2017 Honda CR-V from inside with remote start. The vehicle offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. The leather seats in the vehicle are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. This small suv features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. This small suv has a 4 Cyl, 1.5L high output engine. It is front wheel drive. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this 2017 Honda CR-V is easy with the climate control system. The Honda CR-V contains elegant lines finished with an exquisite green color. Enjoy the convenience of the power liftgate on the vehicle. Help alleviate lower back pain with the driver seat lumbar support in the Honda CR-V.

The turbocharged T6 powertrain paired with Volvos intelligent AWD system delivers confident acceleration and year-round capability, while the R-Design package adds aggressive styling and a sport-tuned feel.

Inside, the Off-Black R-Design sport split leather seating provides premium comfort and support, making this XC60 ideal for daily commuting or long-distance driving. PROBABLY THE BEST DEALERSHIP IN THE WORLD!

This 2017 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited is a true standout in its class, boasting a stunning white exterior and a wealth of premium features that are sure to impress. With its powerful 3.6L V6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and capable 4-wheel drive system, this Grand Cherokee is ready to tackle any adventure with confidence and style.

• NAVIGATION
• BACKUP CAMERA
• FOUR WHEEL DRIVE
• GPS
• BLUETOOTH
• RADIO: UCONNECT 3C NAV W/8.4" DISPLAY
• POWER SUNROOF

The interior of this Grand Cherokee is equally impressive, with luxurious leather-trimmed bucket seats, a heated steering wheel, and a state-of-the-art Uconnect infotainment system that puts a wealth of connectivity and entertainment options at your fingertips. The spacious and versatile cabin offers ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect choice for families or adventurous individuals alike.

Beyond its impressive list of features, this Grand Cherokee also boasts excellent fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 18 city and 25 highway miles per gallon. This combination of power, capability, and efficiency makes it a truly compelling option in the midsize SUV segment.

Whether you're looking for a capable off-road companion, a comfortable daily driver, or a versatile family vehicle, this 2017 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited has everything you need and more. With its impressive array of features, exceptional performance, and unbeatable value, this Grand Cherokee is sure to exceed your expectations.

At our dealership, we take pride in offering our customers the finest selection of pre-owned vehicles, and this 2017 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited is no exception. With a clean CARFAX history report and a thorough inspection by our certified technicians, you can rest assured that this Grand Cherokee is ready to provide you with years of reliable and enjoyable driving.

We invite you to come in and experience this exceptional vehicle for yourself. Our knowledgeable and friendly sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and to help you find the perfect vehicle to meet your needs. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a truly remarkable SUV – visit us today and let us show you why we're PROBABLY THE BEST DEALERSHIP IN THE WORLD!

Discover the exceptional 2017 GMC Acadia Denali, a sophisticated and capable SUV that redefines the driving experience. This stunning vehicle, adorned in a sleek White Frost Tricoat exterior, is equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 engine and advanced all-wheel-drive system, delivering exceptional performance and versatility.

Highlighted features include:
• Dual SkyScape 2-Panel Power Sunroof
• Surround Vision System
• Forward Automatic Braking
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Seats
• Perforated Leather-Appointed Seat Trim
• Power Liftgate
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Experience the ultimate in comfort and convenience with the Acadia Denali's premium amenities. The spacious and well-appointed interior, with seating for up to 6 passengers, offers a refined and luxurious driving environment. Indulge in the soothing ambiance of the dual-zone climate control, the convenience of the power-operated liftgate, and the seamless integration of your smartphone with the advanced IntelliLink infotainment system.

Safety is paramount in the Acadia Denali, which boasts a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. The Surround Vision System provides a 360-degree view around the vehicle, while Forward Automatic Braking helps mitigate the risk of collisions. Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop/Go functionality ensures a smooth and effortless driving experience, even in heavy traffic.

Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and capability in the 2017 GMC Acadia Denali. This exceptional SUV is a true reflection of your discerning taste and active lifestyle. Visit our showroom today to experience the Acadia Denali firsthand and explore the possibilities of owning this remarkable vehicle.

Discover the perfect balance of style, capability, and comfort in this 2017 Toyota RAV4 Limited. This exceptional SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience with its impressive array of advanced features and premium amenities.

Key Highlights:
• AWD
• Back-Up Camera
• Heated Seats
• Bluetooth Connectivity

This RAV4 Limited is powered by a robust 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC Dual VVT-i engine, delivering a smooth and efficient performance with an impressive 22 city/29 highway MPG. The 6-Speed Automatic transmission and all-wheel-drive system provide confident handling and exceptional control, making this SUV a joy to drive in any condition.

Inside, you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium features that cater to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of Keyless Entry, the comfort of Heated Front Seats, and the peace of mind of a Backup Camera. Stay connected with Bluetooth technology, and keep your hands on the wheel with Steering Wheel-Mounted Controls.

The RAV4 Limited also boasts a stunning array of safety and technology features, including Front Dual-Zone Climate Control, a Power Liftgate, and a Panoramic Moonroof. Cruise with confidence thanks to Active Cruise Control, and stay secure with Electronic Stability Control and ABS Brakes.

Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2017 Toyota RAV4 Limited. This SUV is the perfect blend of style, capability, and comfort, making it an outstanding choice for those seeking a versatile and feature-rich vehicle. Visit our showroom today and discover the true potential of this remarkable RAV4.

description:
Introducing the ultimate SUV for all your driving needs - the 2017 Ford Explorer Platinum. With its sleek design, powerful performance, and luxurious features, this vehicle is sure to impress.

Under the hood, you'll find a robust EcoBoost 3.5L Twin Turbo V6 engine, capable of delivering an impressive 365 horsepower and 350 lb-ft of torque. This means you'll have the power you need to tackle any road or weather condition with ease.

Paired with a 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, the Explorer Platinum offers a smooth and efficient driving experience. You can easily switch between gears with just the touch of a button, making your daily commute or long road trips a breeze.

Step inside and you'll be greeted with a spacious and upscale interior. The Platinum trim level includes premium leather seats, wood accents, and ambient lighting, creating a sophisticated and comfortable atmosphere for you and your passengers.

But that's not all - this Explorer also comes equipped with the latest technology features to enhance your driving experience. From the SYNC 3 infotainment system to the advanced safety features, you'll have everything you need at your fingertips.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2017 Ford Explorer Platinum. With its impressive performance, luxurious features, and cutting-edge technology, it's the perfect SUV for those who want it all. Visit our dealership today and take it for a test drive. You won't be disappointed.
